    "voice_pack_intro_student": "Ardaygu wuxuu cod kasta ku duubaa codkiisa gaarka ah (wuu u fiican yahay dareenka lahaanshaha iyo tababarka ku dhawaaqida). Taabo 👂 si aad u maqasho tusaalaha marka hore, ka dibna 🎙️ si aad u duubto. Codka ardaygu waa diiwaan sir ah: wuxuu ku haraa qalabkan, \"Dhoofi\"-na wuxuu abuuraa fayl SIR ah oo aad maamusho.",
