      "assessment_checklist": "☑ Liiska hubinta qiimaynta",
      "per_grade_skills_checklists_use_during": "Liisas hubin xirfad oo fasal kasta. Isticmaal inta lagu jiro qiimayn qof-qof ah ama si aad u qorsheyso waxbaridda.",
      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Ilmahaygu wuxuu leeyahay \"Waan necbahay jajabyada\"",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "Aad bay u caansan tahay. Jajabyadu waxay jebiyaan xeerarka ardaydu ku barato tirooyinka dhan — tirooyinka waaweyn had iyo jeer macnaheedu ma aha qiimayaal waaweyn. Xanaaqu waa dhab iyo caadi. Ka caawi: (1) adigoo isticmaalaya qaabab muuqaal ah sida pizza ama xariiqyada jajabka, (2) adigoo ku xiraya nolosha dhabta ah (karinta, waqtiga, lacagta), (3) adigoo ku celceliya wax yar oo joogto ah (5 daqiiqo maalintii) halkii fadhi dheer, (4) adigoo ammaanaya dadaalka, ma aha kaliya jawaabaha saxda ah.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Ilmahaygu ma fahmo SABABTA nidaamyadu u shaqeeyaan",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "Kaligood ma aha — ardayda badankood waxay bartaan nidaamka marka hore, sababta na dib. Ka caawi adigoo had iyo jeer muujinaya sida nidaamku u eg yahay sawir. \"Isku dhufo 3/4 iyo 1/2\" waxaa loo sawiri karaa afargees. Tabka Op Proofs ayaa taas kuu sameeya. Weydii \"maxay?\" si tartiib ah oo joogto ah.",
      "how_can_i_help_with_homework_without_d": "Sideen uga caawin karaa shaqada guriga anigoon u qabanin?",
      "use_the_worked_examples_tab_they_show_": "Isticmaal tabka Worked Examples — waxay muujiyaan nidaamyada tallaabo-tallaabo oo leh sabab. Wada mari dhibaatooyin la mid ah, ma aha isku mid. Haddii ay yiraahdaan \"Ma garanayo sida loo bilaabo,\" weydii \"Maxay dhibaatadu ku weydiisanaysaa inaad hesho? Maxaan hore u naqaan?\" Nidaamka tilmaanta ee Dhibaatooyinka Erayada wuxuu bixiyaa tilmaamo lakab ah — isku day midka hore ka hor jawaabta.",
      "what_should_i_drill": "Maxaan tababaraa?",
      "ies_practice_guide_recommends_1_magnit": "IES Practice Guide wuxuu ku talinayaa: (1) fikirka cabbirka (shaqada xariiqda tirada), (2) xiriirka muuqaalka iyo astaanta, (3) dhibaatooyinka erayada ee macne leh. KA FOGOW: tababbar nidaamyo aan fahan lahayn. Ku bixi 5 daqiiqo Benchmark Trainer, 5 Dhibaatooyinka Erayada, iyo 5 ciyaar — taasi waa fadhi 15-daqiiqo oo fiican.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Ilmahaygu wuxuu saxaa nidaamka laakiin jawaabtu waa khaldan tahay",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Badanaa waxay ka dhigan tahay qalad xisaabeed yar (tusaale, isku dhuftay khalad) ama ma fududayn. Tus Cheat Sheet — waxay hubin karaan shaqadooda tallaabo-tallaabo. Ku dhiirrigeli inay ku xaqiijiyaan hab kale (marka hore qiyaas, ama isticmaal qaab kale).",
      "what_if_i_don_t_remember_fractions_wel": "Ka warran haddii aan anigu si fiican u xasuusan jajabyada?",
      "you_don_t_have_to_be_the_expert_use_th": "Uma baahnid inaad khabiir noqoto! Isticmaal Tab Guide iyo Worked Examples — waxay si cad u sharraxaan nidaamyada. Ka fiican: tus \"aan wada ogaano tan.\" Waad la baran kartaa ilmahaaga. Tabka Erayada wuu faa'iido leeyahay xitaa dadka waaweyn.",
      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Sideen u ogaan karaa haddii ilmahaygu jidka saaran yahay?",
      "look_at_the_standards_tab_to_see_which": "Eeg tabka Standards si aad u aragto heerarka CCSS ee ay tahay inay ogaadaan fasalkooda. Tabka Mastery wuxuu muujiyaa horumarka. Hubin degdeg ah: ma sawiri karaan (a) qaab 3/4, (b) sheegi karaan jajab u dhigma 1/2, (c) isbarbardhigi karaan 2/3 iyo 3/4 oo sharraxi karaan? Saddexdaas tijaabo waxay daboolaan filashooyinka jajabka K-5 badankooda.",
      "parent_guide": "👨‍👩‍👧 Hagaha waalidka",
      "guidance_for_parents_helping_kids_with": "Hagitaan waalidiinta caawinaya carruurta jajabyada guriga. Caqabadaha caadiga ah, talooyin la taaban karo, iyo waxa la weydiiyo.",
      "the_why_of_learning_recruiting_interes": "\"SABABTA\" waxbarashada — soo-jiidashada xiisaha, joogtaynta dadaalka, is-xakameynta",
