      "exam_prep_practice_tests": "📝 Diyaargarowga imtixaanka — imtixaanno celcelin",
      "multiple_choice_quizzes_that_mirror_st": "Imtixaanno doorasho-badan ah oo muujiya qaabka imtixaanka heer-siman. Dooro heer fasal, qaado imtixaan 10-su'aal ah, arag dhibcahaaga.",
