      "last_14_days": "14-kii maalmood ee la soo dhaafay:",
      "the_1_2_trick": "Xeeladda 1/2",
      "let_your_number_be_n_the_sequence_n_1_": "Ha tiradaadu ahaato n. Taxanaha: (n+1) × 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n + 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n. Qaybi 2 → n. Ka jar asalka → 0. Sug — taasi waxay siisaa 0, ma aha 1. Isku day: n → (n+1)×2 = 2n+2 → +4 = 2n+6 → −6 = 2n → ÷2 = n → −asalka = 0. \"Xeeladdu\" waxay ku tiirsan tahay constants qarsoon oo taxanaha ku jira.",
      "sum_of_unit_fractions": "Wadarta jajabyada unug",
      "each_term_is_half_the_previous_the_tot": "Eray kastaa waa badh kii hore. Wadartu waxay u dhowaataa 1 laakiin weligeed ma gaadho. Kani waa taxane geometric aan dhammaad lahayn oo leh eray kowaad 1/2 iyo saami 1/2: S = (1/2) / (1 − 1/2) = 1. Tan awgeed ayaa paradox-ka dhaqdhaqaaqa ee Zeno xisaab ahaan loo xallin karaa.",
      "the_harmonic_series": "Taxanaha harmonic",
      "even_though_each_term_is_small_the_ser": "In kasta oo eray kastaa yar yahay, taxanahu wuu kala firdhaa. Si aad u gaadho 100, waxaad u baahan tahay qiyaastii 1.5 × 10^43 eray. Tan waxaa caddeeyay Nicole Oresme 1300-meeyadii isticmaalka kooxaynta: 1/3 + 1/4 > 1/4 + 1/4 = 1/2; 1/5+...+1/8 > 4 × 1/8 = 1/2; had iyo jeer waad heli kartaa 1/2 kale oo aad ku darto.",
      "farey_sequences": "Taxanayaasha Farey",
      "check_1_4_and_1_3_4_1_1_3_1_check_2_5_": "Hubi 1/4 iyo 1/3: (4)(1) − (1)(3) = 1. Hubi 2/5 iyo 1/2: (5)(1) − (2)(2) = 1. Sifadan waxay abuurtaa geedka Stern-Brocot ee dhammaan tirooyinka macquulka ah.",
      "multiplying_telescopes": "Telescopes isku-dhufan",
      "rewrite_1_2_2_3_3_4_n_1_n_the_2_in_2_3": "Dib u qor: 1/2 × 2/3 × 3/4 × ... × (n−1)/n. 2-da ku jirta 2/3 waxay tirtirtaa 2-da ku jirta tirada hoose ee 1/2. 3-da ku jirta 3/4 waxay tirtirtaa 3-da ku jirta tirada hoose ee 2/3. Wax kastaa waa la tirtiraa marka laga reebo 1/n.",
      "fraction_magic_tricks": "🎩 Xeeladaha sixirka jajabka",
      "mathematical_tricks_that_are_really_el": "\"Xeelado\" xisaabeed oo dhab ahaantii ah aqoonsiyo jajab oo qurux badan. Dooro mid si aad u aragto dejinta, muujinta, iyo sharraxaadda xisaabeed.",
