      "average_of_1_4_and_1_2_is_1_4_1_2_2_1_": "Celceliska 1/4 iyo 1/2 waa (1/4 + 1/2) / 2 = (1 + 2)/8 = 3/8.",
      "pizza_slicing": "Gooynta pizza",
