      "common_core_fluency_automatic_recall_o": "Fasaaxadda Common Core = xusuusin toos ah oo xaqiiqooyinka aasaasiga ah in ka yar 3 ilbiriqsi. Qaabka pizza waxa-ka-mid-ah-dhan; qaabka baar isbarbardhig iyo hawlgal.",
      "compare_cross_multiply_or_benchmark": "Isbarbardhig — isku dhufo iskutallaab ama benchmark",
      "three_tools_same_denom_just_compare_to": "Saddex qalab: tirada hoose isku mid (kaliya isbarbardhig kuwa sare), isku-dhufasho-iskutallaab (a/b iyo c/d → ad iyo bc), ama benchmark ½ / ¾. Kan ugu dambeeya ayaa ugu dhaqso badan madaxaaga.",
      "operations_add_sub_mul_div_with_rules": "Hawlgallo — ku dar/ka jar/isku dhufo/qaybi xeerar leh",
      "add_sub_common_denominator_first_multi": "Ku dar/ka jar: tirada hoose ee guud marka hore. Isku dhufo: sare×sare, hoose×hoose. Qaybi: hay-beddel-rogo (isku dhufo reciprocal). Had iyo jeer u fududee erayada ugu hooseeya.",
      "equivalents_same_value_different_form": "Kuwa u dhigma — qiime isku mid, qaab kala duwan",
      "multiply_top_and_bottom_by_the_same_nu": "Isku dhufo sare IYO hoose isla tiro; qiimuhu wuu sii jiraa. ½ = 2/4 = 50/100 = 0.5 = 50%. Jajabyada u dhigma waa buundada u dhexeysa jajabyada, decimalka, iyo boqolkiibada.",
      "converter_mixed_improper_decimal": "Beddele — isku-dhafan ↔ aan habboonayn ↔ decimal",
      "2_11_4_long_division_gives_a_terminati": "2¾ = 11/4. Qaybinta dheer waxay bixisaa decimal dhammaanaya (tirada hoose = 2¹ × 5ⁿ) ama mid soo noqnoqda (tiro-bilaash kasta oo kale oo tirada hoose ku jira). 1/3 = 0.333... weligeed.",
      "wall_visual_proof_of_equivalence": "Derbi — caddaynta muuqaal ee isu-dhigmidka",
      "stack_the_fraction_wall_1_whole_2_halv": "Isku dul-dhig derbiga jajabka: 1 dhan = 2 badhabo = 4 rubuc = 8 sideed-meelood. Dherer isku mid = qiime isku mid. Ulaha Cuisenaire (1952) tan waxay ka dhigeen mid taabasho ah; derbigu waa faraca dhijitaalka ah.",
      "equals_exactly_1_whole": "🟢 Waxay la mid tahay si sax ah 1 dhan",
