      "keyframes_coinflip_0_transform_scalex_": "@keyframes coinFlip{0%{transform:scaleX(1)}25%{transform:scaleX(0.05) translateY(-10px)}60%{transform:scaleX(1.08) translateY(-4px)}100%{transform:scaleX(1) translateY(0)}} @keyframes diceRoll{0%{transform:rotate(0deg)scale(1)}25%{transform:rotate(-24deg)scale(1.12)}55%{transform:rotate(19deg)scale(1.08)}80%{transform:rotate(-8deg)scale(1.04)}100%{transform:rotate(0deg)scale(1)}} @keyframes resultPop{0%{transform:scale(0.78);opacity:0.35}55%{transform:scale(1.09);opacity:1}100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}} @keyframes sportBounce{0%{transform:translateY(0)scale(1)}40%{transform:translateY(-20px)scale(1.12)}70%{transform:translateY(-6px)scale(1.06)}100%{transform:translateY(0)scale(1)}}",
      "back_to_tools": "Ku noqo Qalabka",
      "probability_lab": "🎲 Shaybaarka Suurtagalnimada",
      "explore_probability_through_experiment": "Sahaminaya suurtagalnimada iyada oo loo marayo tijaabooyin. Socodsii tijaabooyin oo arag inta jeer ee la arkay oo ku soo dhowaanaya qiyamka la filayo.",
      "coin_the_simplest_50_50": "Qadaadiic — 50/50 ugu fudud",
      "p_h_p_t_0_5_law_of_large_numbers_as_tr": "P(H) = P(T) = 0.5. Sharciga tirooyinka waaweyn: marka tijaabooyinku kordhaan, saamiga madaxa wuxuu ku soo dhowaadaa 0.5. Ka dib 1,000 tuujin waxaad ku jiri doontaa ~3% gudaha 50%, laakiin taxane gaaban kasta wax kastaa wuu suurtagal yahay.",
      "dice_uniform_1_n_each_d4_d6_d8_d10_d12": "Laadhuu — mid kasta sinnaan 1/N (d4 / d6 / d8 / d10 / d12 / d20)",
      "pick_any_die_size_each_face_equally_li": "Dooro cabbir kasta oo laadhuu. Wajigii kasta si siman ayuu u suurtagal yahay: P = 1/N. Xisaabtu way isku mid tahay dhammaan noocyada laadhuuga — waxa is beddelaa waa hoosaadka. d4 waa 1/4, d20 waa 1/20.",
      "two_dice_sum_the_triangular_distributi": "Wadarta laba laadhuu — qaybinta saddex-xagal",
      "roll_two_dice_of_the_chosen_type_and_a": "Tuuji laba laadhuu oo nooca la doortay oo isku dar. Wadartu hadda ma sinna: wadarta dhexe aad bay u caansan tahay. 2d6, P(7)=6/36, P(2)=1/36. Sababtaas awgeed ayaa Monopoly dadku ugu badan ku degaan hantida liinta — ka dib ka soo bixista xabsiga, 6, 7, 8 waa wadarta ugu caansan.",
      "spinner_4_color_uniform": "Wareejiye — 4-midab sinnaan",
      "equal_area_sectors_equal_probability_u": "Qaybo bedka siman = suurtagalnimo siman. Qaybo aan sinnayn → soo-saaris culus. Wareejiyayaashu waa jidka ugu jilicsan ee ardayda hoose ee xagga qaybinta gooni-gooni ah.",
      "sports_weighted_real_world_odds": "Ciyaaraha — fursadaha culus ee adduunka dhabta ah",
      "free_throw_75_nba_3_point_36_mlb_hit_2": "Tuujada bilaashka ah 75%, saddex-dhibic NBA 36%, garaac MLB ~25%. Suurtagalnimadu had iyo jeer maaha 50/50 — xisaabtu waxay u maamushaa miisaanka aan sinnayn si la mid ah, kaliya hoosaad kala duwan.",
      "marble_bag_with_vs_without_replacement": "Bac dhagax-yari — beddelaad la' iyo la-leh",
      "with_replacement_independent_draws_wit": "Beddelaad la-leh: soo-saaris madax-banaan. La'aan: suurtagalnimadu way is beddeshaa soo-saaris kasta — suurtagalnimo shuruudaysan. Habka saxda ah ee ka dambeeya qaybinta hipergeometric iyo fursadaha ciyaaraha turubka.",
      "custom_design_your_own_outcome_set": "Gaar — naqshadee koox natiijooyin oo aad leedahay",
      "build_any_discrete_distribution_test_t": "Dhis qaybin kasta oo gooni-gooni ah. Tijaabi sharciga tirooyinka waaweyn fursado leexsan, muuji in tijaabooyin ku filan ay jeexitaanku ka jawaabi karo su'aal kasta oo qaab-xiran ah. Monte Carlo yar.",
      "tree_multi_stage_probability": "Geed — suurtagalnimo marxalado-badan",
      "multiply_along_branches_add_across_lea": "Ku dhufo laamaha; ku dar caleemaha dhexdooda. Laba tuujin qadaadiic: HH HT TH TT mid kasta 0.25. Jaantusyada geedku waxay fidaan ilaa dhibaatooyinka heerka aasaasiga ah ee tijaabooyinka caafimaadka iyo aragtida Bayes.",
      "pi_monte_carlo_estimation": "Pi — qiyaasta Monte Carlo π",
      "throw_darts_at_a_unit_square_count_how": "Tuuji fallaadho afargees cabbir ah; tiri inta ku dhacaysa gudaha rubuc-goobeed ku qoran. π ≈ 4 × (gudaha / wadar). Ku-soo-dhowaanshuhu waa O(1/√N) — lambar kasta wuxuu ku kacaa fallaadho 100× badan.",
      "birthday_the_famous_paradox": "Dhalashada — caqligalnimada caanka ah",
      "in_a_room_of_23_the_probability_of_a_s": "Qol 23 qof ah, suurtagalnimada dhalasho la wadaago waa > 50%. 70 waa > 99.9%. Lid ku ah dareenka sababtoo ah waxaynu tirinnaa is-barbardhigyo (2 ka mid ah 23 = 253), ma aha dadka. Tusaalaha lidka ah ee ugu cad fasalka ee suurtagalnimada dareenka.",
      "marble_bag_setup": "🎱 Habaynta Bacda Dhagax-yarida",
      "without_replacement_each_marble_drawn_": "💡 Beddelaad la'aan: dhagax-yar kasta oo la soo saaray waa laga saaraa bacda. Suurtagalnimadu way is beddeshaa soo-saaris kasta ka dib! Bacdu way buuxsantaa marka ay madhan tahay.",
