      "the_point_at_1_4_is_the_same_point_as_": "Barta 1/4 waa barta isku mid ah ee 0.25. Goob isku mid ah, laba magac.",
      "some_terminate_some_repeat": "Qaar way dhammaadaan, qaar way isku celcelinayaan. ",
      "1_2_0_5_stops_1_4_0_25_stops_1_3_0_333": "1/2 = 0.5 (way joogsadaa). 1/4 = 0.25 (way joogsadaa). 1/3 = 0.333… (weligeed isku celcelinaysa). Hoostu way go'aamisaa: haddii ay u kala baxdo 2 iyo 5 oo keliya, way dhammaataa. Haddii kale way isku celcelinaysaa. Fiiri calaamadda ↻ kaarka jajab-tobanka.",
