      "two_fractions_four_possible_relationsh": "Laba jajab, afar xiriir oo suurtagal ah: siman, taabanaya calaamadda ½, A ka yar ama B ka yar. Jiid sliders-ka, qor waxa aad ogaato, oo qor xeerkaaga isbarbardhigga.",
