      "the_s_ivb_third_stage_will_fire_for_5_": "Marxaladda saddexaad ee S-IVB waxay shidan doontaa 5 daqiiqo 47 ilbiriqsi si ay xawaaraha uga kordhiso km 28,000/saac ilaa km 38,900/saac — xawaaraha baxsiga. Shididdan keliya ayaa kuu dirta jid u sii jeedda Dayaxa oo u jira km 384,400.",
      "execute_trans_lunar_injection_burn_to_": "Fuli shidista Trans-Lunar Injection si aad u bilowdo safar 3 maalmood ah ee Dayaxa",
