      "begin_atmospheric_re_entry_sequence_at": "Bilow isku-xigxiga dib-u-galitaanka jawiga km 39,900 saacaddii",
      "begin_re_entry_sequence": "🌊 Bilow Isku-xigxiga Dib-u-galitaanka",
      "animated_re_entry_sequence_command_mod": "Isku-xigxiga dib-u-galitaanka ee dhaqdhaqaaqa leh. Qaybta amarka waxay gashaa jawiga km 39,900/saac oo leh kuleylka plasma ilaa darajo 2,760. Wuxuu muujiyaa go'idda raadiyaha, baarashuudaha hore, baarashuudaha waaweyn, iyo ku degitaanka biyaha badda.",
      "watch_the_command_module_survive_re_en": "Daawo qaybta amarka oo ka badbaadaysa dib-u-galitaanka iyada oo loo marayo plasma 2,760°C ah km 39,900/saac, oo furaysa baarashuudaha, oo ku degaysa Badweynta Baasifigga.",
      "complete_the_mission_with_pacific_ocea": "Dhammaystir hawsha adigoo ku degaya biyaha Badweynta Baasifigga. Ku soo dhowow guriga, Taliye!",
