      "eyewash_station_located_2": "🚿 Xarunta dhaqista isha waa la helay!",
      "the_10_second_rule_if_chemicals_splash": "Xeerka 10-ilbiriqsi: haddii kiimikaad ku saydho indhahaaga, waxaad haysataa qiyaastii 10 ilbiriqsi si aad u gaadho xarunta dhaqista isha ka hor inta uusan bilaaban dhaawaca joogtada ah. Indhaha furan hayso oo dhaq 15+ daqiiqo.",
      "fire_extinguisher_located_2": "🧯 Dab-demiska waa la helay!",
      "remember_p_a_s_s_pull_the_pin_aim_at_b": "Xasuuso P.A.S.S.: Pull (Jiid biinka), Aim (U hagaaji saldhigga dabka), Squeeze (Riix qabashada), Sweep (Ka fayd dhinac ilaa dhinaca kale). Aashitada acetic iyo qaar ka mid ah dareerayaasha way ololayaan — ogow meeshan ka hor inta aadan bilaabin.",
      "safety_data_sheets_located": "📋 Warqadaha macluumaadka badbaadada waa la helay!",
      "sds_documents_list_all_hazards_require": "Dokumentiyada SDS waxay liistaan dhammaan khataraha, qalabka ilaalinta loo baahan yahay, tallaabooyinka gargaarka koowaad, iyo xiriirrada degdegga ah ee kiimikaad kasta oo shaybaadhka ku jira. Baar iyaga ka hor inta aadan maareyn kiimikaad kasta.",
