      "dilution_calc": "🧮 Xisaabiyaha khafiifinta",
      "buffers": "🛡️ Buffer",
      "titrate_find_the_equivalence_point": "Titration samee — Hel dhibcaha sinnaanta",
      "add_titrant_drop_by_drop_until_indicat": "Ku dar titrant dhibic-dhibic ilaa tilmaamuhu beddelo midabka. Dhibcaha sinnaanta = dheelitir stoichiometric; dhibcaha dhammaadka = halka tilmaamuhu beddelayo. Had iyo jeer isku mid maaha.",
      "challenge_graded_titrations": "Caqabad — Titration-yo qiimeeyay",
      "match_real_world_unknowns_by_titrating": "U dhig waxyaabaha aan la garanayn ee adduunka dhabta ah adigoo titration u samaynaya ilaa ±0.05 ml qiimaha aragtiyeed. La soco saxnaanta + xawaaraha; qiimeynta waxay la mid tahay AP Chem.",
      "safety_drills_what_could_go_wrong": "Tababarrada badbaadada — Maxaa qaldami kara",
      "burette_explodes_acid_burns_spill_indi": "Biuret wuu qarxaa, daadin gubasho aashito, tilmaame si degdeg ah loo daray. Ku tababaro isku-xigxiga jawaab-celinta saxda ah ka hor inta uu muhiim ka noqon shaybaadhka dhabta ah.",
      "equipment_burette_flask_pipette": "Qalab — Biuret, flask, pipette",
      "burette_tolerance_0_05_ml_volumetric_f": "Dul-qaadka biuret 0.05 ml; flask mugga 0.10 ml; pipette 0.02 ml. Fasalka saxnaanta A ee ka soo horjeeda B wuxuu labanlaabaa qaladka. Habaynta ayaa muhiim ka ah sida ardaydu u malaynayaan.",
      "dilution_calculator_m_v_m_v": "Xisaabiyaha khafiifinta — M₁V₁ = M₂V₂",
      "stock_diluent_desired_concentration_th": "Kayd + khafiifiye → tirada la rabo. 4-ta dhibaato ee AP Chem ee ugu badan la tijaabiyo waxay ku soo dhacaan isla'eg keliya kan. La soco tirooyinka muhiimka ah: cabbirka ugu daciifsan ayaa go'aamiya jawaabta.",
      "buffer_discovery_when_does_a_buffer_ho": "Ogaanshaha buffer — Goorma ayaa buffer sii jira?",
      "adjust_acid_strength_a_ha_ratio_starti": "Hagaaji xoogga aashitada, saamiga [A⁻]/[HA], iyo pH bilowga. Natiijadu way kala duwan tahay: buffer wanaagsan ama buffer xun (ka dib ku darista aashito dheeraad ah 20%). Ma jiro qiimo, ma jiro daahfur — kaliya baaris iyo indho-indhayn.",
      "endpoint_equivalence": "⚠ Dhibcaha dhammaadka ≠ dhibcaha sinnaanta. ",
