      "energy_inquiry": "Baaritaanka Tamarta",
      "read_v_formation_explanation_aloud": "Akhri sharraxaadda qaabka V si cod dheer",
      "read_aloud": "🔊 Akhri Cod Dheer",
      "v_formation_simulator_canvas_drag_bird": "Kanfaska jilaaga qaabka V. Jiid shimbiraha si aad u beddesho meelahooda. Shimbirta hoggaaminaysa waxaa lagu calaamadeeyay xiddig. Baararka tamarta ee ka sarreeya shimbir kasta waxay muujinayaan heerka tamarta hadda. Koonaha cagaaran ee ka dambeeya shimbir kasta waxay muujinayaan aagagga hawo-kor, halkaas oo shimbiraha dambe ay tamarta ku badbaadinayaan. Aagga guduudan ee si toos ah u dambeeya wuxuu muujinayaa aagga hawo-hoos.",
      "auto_form_v_formation": "Si toos ah u samee qaabka V",
      "auto_form_v": "🪿 Samee V",
