      "when_a_bird_flaps_its_wings_it_creates": "Marka shimbir garabkiisa ruxo, waxay abuurtaa dabayl wareegaysa oo ku taal cidhibta garab kasta. Hawada si toos ah uga dambeysa oo ka hoosaysa cidhibta garabka waxaa hoos loo riixaa ",
      "downwash_but_the_air_to_the_side_pushe": " (hawo-hoos), laakiin hawada dhinaca ku taal kor baa loo riixaa ",
      "by_positioning_themselves_in_the_upwas": "Iyagoo naftooda dhigaya aagga hawo-kor — qiyaastii 30° ka dambeeya oo dhinac ka ah shimbirta hore — shimbiraha dambe waxay helaan taageero bilaash ah oo ka timaadda hawada kor u kacaysa. Raxamada dhabta ah tan waxay badbaadisaa qiyaastii ",
      "of_their_energy": " tamartooda (",
      "is_a_theoretical_maximum": " waa xadka aragtiyeed ee ugu badan).",
      "the_leader_gets_no_benefit_and_tires_f": "Hoggaamiyaha wax faa'iido ah kama helo wuxuuna daalaa si dhaqso ah. Marka tamartiisu ka hoos dhacdo 30%, wuu dib u gadaal socdaa oo shimbir kale ayaa qaata hoggaanka. Tan waxaa loo yaqaan ",
      "leader_rotation": "wareega hoggaanka",
      "in_nature_every_bird_takes_a_turn_at_t": ". Dabeecadda dhexdeeda shimbir kastaa wuxuu qaataa marxaladdiisa hore.",
      "try_dragging_birds_into_different_posi": "Isku day inaad shimbiraha u jiiddo meelo kala duwan si aad u aragto sida waxtarka qaabka iyo badbaadinta tamarta u beddelmaan! Riix V si aad si toos ah u samayso, S si aad u kala firdhiso.",
      "formation_science": "🔬 Sayniska Qaabaynta",
      "migration_world_records": "🏆 Diiwaanka Adduunka ee Socdaalka",
      "energy_budget_calculator": "⚡ Xisaabiyaha Miisaaniyadda Tamarta",
      "adjust_the_sliders_to_see_how_distance": "Hagaaji sliderrada si aad u aragto sida masaafada, cabbirka jirka, dabaysha iyo qaabku u saameeyaan baahiyaha tamarta shimbir. Tan waxay ku dayanaysaa fiisigiska dhabta ah ee duulimaadka socdaalka.",
      "kcal_needed": "kcal loo baahan yahay",
      "fat_required": "Baruur loo baahan yahay",
      "of_body_weight": "miisaanka jirka",
      "insects_equivalent": "U dhigma Cayayaan",
      "the_science": "Sayniska: ",
      "bird_flight_costs_12x_their_resting_me": "Duulimaadka shimbir wuxuu ku kacaa qiyaastii 12 jeer heerka dheef-shiid kiimikaad ee nasashada (sharciga Kleiber). Baruurtu waxay bixisaa 9 kcal halkii garaam — shidaal tamar-badan oo ugu sarreeya bayoolajiga. Ka hor socdaalka shimbiraha waxay galaan ",
      "a_feeding_frenzy_where_they_may_double": " — cunto-badan, halkaas oo ay ku laba-labayn karaan miisaanka jirkooda baruur. Bar-tailed Godwit wuxuu gubaa ",
      "55_of_its_body_weight": "55% miisaanka jirkiisa",
      "during_its_7_145_mile_non_stop_flight_": " inta lagu jiro duulimaadkiisa mayl 7,145 oo aan istaag lahayn ee ka socda Alaska ilaa New Zealand.",
      "this_journey_requires_more_fat_than_th": "⚠️ Safarkani wuxuu u baahan yahay baruur ka badan miisaanka shimbirka! Wuxuu u baahan doonaa goobo shidaal-buuxin ah — ama qaabka V si loo yareeyo kharashka.",
      "altitude_physiology": "✈️ Fiisiyoolajiga Dhererka",
      "some_birds_migrate_at_extreme_altitude": "Shimbiro qaar waxay ku socdaalaan dherer aad u xad-dhaaf ah — Bar-headed Geese waxay ka gudbaan Himalaya cag 29,000. Jiid slider-ka si aad u aragto sida xaaladuhu u beddelmaan.",
      "air_density": "Cufnaanta Hawada",
      "wind": "Dabayl",
      "extreme_altitude": "Dherer xad-dhaaf ah! ",
      "bar_headed_geese_survive_here_thanks_t": "Bar-headed Geese waxay halkan ku noolaadaan hemoglobin si xoog leh u xidha ogsijiinta, sambabo waaweyn iyo mitochondria hufan. Naasleyda badankood way suuxi lahaayeen dhererkan. Dhiiggoodu wuxuu leeyahay isbeddel gaar ah oo hemoglobin ah (Pro→Ala boqorka 119) kaas oo kordhiya soo-jiidashada ogsijiinta 50%.",
      "high_altitude_zone": "Aagga dherer sare. ",
      "many_songbirds_migrate_at_this_range_w": "Shimbiro badan oo heesa ah waxay ku socdaalaan xadkan, halkaas oo hawada khafiifka ah ay yareyso jiidashada laakiin ogsijiintu yar tahay. Shimbiruhu tan waxay ku magdhabaan neefsasho hufan: nidaamkooda hawo-socodka hal-jiho ah wuxuu ogsijiinta soo saaraa marka la neefsanayo iyo marka la sii deynayo, oo ka duwan sambabbada naasleyda oo soo saara kaliya marka la neefsanayo.",
      "common_cruising_altitude": "Dhererka safar caadi ah. ",
      "most_migrants_fly_between_5_000_15_000": "Socdaalayaasha badankood waxay duulaan inta u dhaxaysa cag 5,000 iyo 15,000. Heerkulka hawadu wuxuu hoos u dhacaa qiyaastii 3.5 °F cag kasta 1,000 (gradient heerkul caadi ah). Shimbiruhu waxay doortaan dhererka si ay u helaan dabaylo wanaagsan — isla shimbirku wuxuu duuli karaa cag 2,000 hal habeen iyo cag 12,000 habeenka xiga.",
      "low_altitude": "Dherer hoose. ",
      "hummingbirds_and_some_shorebirds_fly_c": "Hummingbird iyo shimbiro xeebeed qaar waxay u duulaan meel u dhow dusha, gaar ahaan biyaha korkooda. Duulimaadka hoose wuu ka badbaadaa barafowga, laakiin waxay ka dhigan tahay iska-caabbin hawo badan iyo taageero dabayl yar. Marka ay ka gudbayaan Gulf of Mexico oo mayl 600 ah, shimbiraha badankood waxay duulaan inta u dhaxaysa cag 1,000 iyo 3,000.",
      "mountain": "Buur",
      "deflects_wind_upward_on_windward_side": "waxay kor u weecisaa dabaysha dhinaca dabaysha soo horyaal",
