      "clear_all": "🗑️ Nadiifi Dhammaan",
      "wind_direction": "Jihada Dabaysha",
      "wind_2": "🌬️ Dabayl:",
      "wind_science_for_migrators": "🌬️ Sayniska Dabaysha ee Socdaalayaasha",
      "thermals": "Qulqulka Kulaylka",
      "thermals_are_columns_of_rising_warm_ai": "Qulqulka kulaylku waa tiirar hawo diirran oo kor u kacaya oo la abuuro marka qorraxdu carrada si aan sinnayn u kululayso. Dusha madoow (meelaha baabuurta la dhigto, beeraha la falay) waxay abuurtaa qulqullo ka xoog badan dusha khafiifka ah (biyaha, kaymaha). Shimbiraha duula sida gorgorrada iyo baqooyinka waxay kor ugu duulaan wareeg qulqulka kulaylka, iyagoo dherer helaya iyagoon garab ruxin. Ka dib waxay u simbiriyaan qulqulka xiga, iyagoo abuuraya “waddo weyn oo kulayl ah”, waddo dhaqso ah oo tamar-badbaadis ah oo cirka ah.",
      "orographic_lift": "Kor-u-qaadka Buuraha",
      "when_wind_encounters_a_mountain_it_is_": "Marka dabayshu buur la kulanto, kor baa loo riixaa jiirka dabaysha soo horyaal. Tan waxay abuurtaa xarig hawo kor u kacaysa oo shimbiraha duula (sida gorgorrada dahabka ah) ay isticmaalaan buuraha korkooda. Dhinaca aan dabaysha soo horyaalin, hawadu si dhaqso ah bay u dhacdaa, iyadoo abuuraysa aag khatar ah oo “rotor” ah oo hawo qallafsan oo hoos u dhacaysa. Taasi waa sababta shimbiraha iyo duuliyayaashu ay uga fogaadaan dhinaca aan dabaysha soo horyaalin ee buuraha.",
      "sea_breezes": "Dabaylaha Badda",
      "land_heats_faster_than_water_during_th": "Dhulku wuu ka kululaadaa si dhaqso ah biyaha maalinta. Hawada diirran waxay kor ugu kacdaa dhulka korkiisa hawada qaboowna waxay ka timaaddaa badda si ay u qaadato meesheeda, iyadoo abuuraysa “dabayl badeed” oo xeebta u socota. Habeenkii qaabku wuu rogmadaa. Shimbiraha socdaalka waxay isticmaalaan dabaylahan xeebeed ee la saadaalin karo si ay tamarta u badbaadiyaan. Aagga isku-imaatinka, halkaas oo dabaysha badda ay la kulanto hawada gudaha, wuxuu inta badan abuuraa qulqulka kulaylka oo shimbiruhu isticmaalaan si ay dherer u helaan.",
      "jet_streams": "Qulqulka Jet",
      "high_altitude_jet_streams_are_narrow_b": "Qulqulka jet-ka dherer sare waa xariijimo cidhiidhi ah oo dabayl aad u dheereeya (100-200 mph) oo cag 30,000-40,000 ah. In kasta oo shimbiraha badankood ay ka duulaan meel aad uga hooseysa qulqulka jet-ka, socdaalayaal qaar sida Bar-tailed Godwit waxay kor u kacaan cag 20,000 si ay u qabtaan dabaylo wanaagsan oo dherer sare ah. Baqooyinka waxaa lagu ogaaday radaar cag 29,000 oo ka sarreeya Himalaya, halkaas oo ogsijiintu yar tahay heerkulkuna uu hoos ugu dhaco -50 °F.",
      "wind_shear": "Gooska Dabaysha",
      "wind_shear_is_a_sudden_change_in_wind_": "Gooska dabayshu waa isbeddel kedis ah oo ku dhaca xawaaraha ama jihada dabaysha meel gaaban. Waa khatar shimbiraha iyo dayuuradaha labadaba. Inta lagu jiro duufaannada, qarxinta yaryar (tiirar kedis ah oo hawo hoos u dhacaysa) waxay abuurtaa goos dabayl xoog leh oo dhulka u dhow. Shimbiruhu waxay dareemaan isbeddellada cadaadiska waxayna inta badan dib u dhigaan socdaalka marka wejiyada duufaanku soo dhowaadaan.",
      "beaufort_scale": "Miisaanka Beaufort",
      "admiral_sir_francis_beaufort_created_h": "Admiral Sir Francis Beaufort wuxuu miisaankiisa dabaysha abuuray 1805 isagoo ku salaysan saameynta dabaysha ee doonyaha shiraaca leh. Miisaanka Beaufort ee casriga ah wuxuu isticmaalaa indha-indhaynta dhulka: xoog 0 (deggan) = qiiqu si toosan buu kor u kacaa; xoog 6 (dabayl xoog leh) = laamaha waaweyn way ruxmaan, dallada way rogmaan; xoog 12 (duufaan) = burbur. Shimbiraha badankood waxay doorbidaan inay socdaalaan xoog 2-4 (dabayl fudud ilaa dhexdhexaad).",
      "how_birds_use_wind": "🐦 Sida Shimbiruhu u Isticmaalaan Dabaysha",
      "tail_winds": "Dabaylaha Dambe: ",
      "migrants_strongly_prefer_flying_with_t": "Socdaalayaashu si xoog leh bay u doorbidaan inay duulaan iyagoo dabayshu ka danbeyso. Xataa dabayl dambe oo 15 mph ah waxay si hufan u laba-labaysaa xawaaraha shimbirka ee dhulka kharash tamar isku mid ah. Daraasaduhu waxay muujinayaan dhaqdhaqaaqa shimbiraha inuu 10 jeer ka badan yahay maalmaha socdaalka ee leh dabaylo dambe oo wanaagsan marka loo eego maalmaha dabaysha hore.",
      "dynamic_soaring": "Duulimaad Firfircoon: ",
      "albatrosses_exploit_wind_speed_gradien": "Albatrosku waxay ka faa'iidaystaan gradient-ka xawaaraha dabaysha ee mowjadaha badda korkooda. Iyagoo isu beddelaya inta u dhaxaysa kor u kaca hawada dhaqso iyo hoos u dhaca hawada gaabis ah oo dusha u dhow, waxay tamarta ka soo saaraan gooska dabaysha lafteeda. Albatros wuxuu duuli karaa kumanaan mayl isagoon garab ruxin qiyaas ahaan.",
      "slope_soaring": "Duulimaad Jiir: ",
      "when_wind_hits_a_cliff_face_or_ridge_t": "Marka dabayshu ku dhufato wejiga jiifka ama tiirka, hawada dib u soo noqonaysa waxay abuurtaa “mowjad” kor-u-qaad ah oo raacaysa xariiqda tiirka. Shimbiraha ugaadhsiga waxay ku duulaan qulqullada tiirkan inta lagu jiro socdaalka, iyagoo isku xidha silsiladaha buuraha sida boodada dhagaxyada. Hawk Mountain oo Pennsylvania ku taal caan bay ku tahay ifafaalahan.",
      "experiment_place_a_thermal_and_a_mount": "Tijaabo: Dhig qulqul kulayl iyo buur bannaanka, kadibna ku dar shimbir. U fiirso isagoo ku duulaya qulqulka kor u kacaya!",
      "birds_as_weather_forecasters": "🌦️ Shimbiraha oo ah Saadaaliyayaasha Cimilada",
      "birds_are_exquisitely_sensitive_to_wea": "Shimbiruhu si aad u xasaasi ah bay u yihiin isbeddellada cimilada waxaana loo isticmaalay sida “barometer nool” taariikhda oo dhan:",
      "barometric_pressure": "Cadaadiska Barometric: ",
      "birds_can_detect_changes_in_barometric": "Shimbiruhu waxay ogaan karaan isbeddellada cadaadiska barometric-ka sababtoo ah qaataayaal gaar ah oo ku yaal dhegta dhexe (xubinta paratympanic). Marka cadaadisku hoos u dhaco duufaanka ka hor, shimbiruhu inta badan hoos bay u duulaan waxayna cunaan si xoog leh. Dab-shimbiraha hoos u duulaya waa astaan duufaan oo caadi ah.",
      "some_birds_can_hear_infrasound_below_2": "Shimbiro qaar waxay maqli karaan infrasound (ka hooseeya 20 Hz) oo laga soo saaro xataa duufaannada fog, mowjadaha badda iyo dhulgariirka. Sida ay ogaadeen dirayaasha GPS, Golden-winged Warblers waxay ka baxeen Tennessee 24 saacadood ka hor inta uusan nidaamka duufaanku iman 2014. Waxay duuleen in ka badan 900 mayl si ay uga fogaadaan duufaannada.",
      "cold_fronts": "Wejiyada Qabow: ",
      "autumn_migration_is_strongly_correlate": "Socdaalka dayrta si xoog leh ayuu ula xiriiraa gudbitaanka wejiyada qabow. Shimbiruhu waxay ku duulaan dabaylaha waqooyi-galbeed ee ka dambeeya wejiyada qabow, kuwaas oo bixiya dabayl dambe iyo cir cad labadaba. Daawadayaasha shimbiraha ee khibradda leh waxay la socdaan khariidadaha cimilada si ay u saadaaliyaan habeennada ugu badan ee socdaalka.",
      "fog_is_dangerous_for_migrating_birds_b": "Ceeryaamadu khatar bay ku tahay shimbiraha socdaalka sababtoo ah waxay qariso calaamadaha dhulka iyo tilmaamaha hagitaanka cirka. Habeennada ceeryaamada leh ee saldhig daruur hoose leh waxay keenaan “dhicid”, halkaas oo shimbiraha socdaalka ee daallan ay raxammo ku degaan deegaanka ugu horreeya ee la heli karo. Dhacdooyinkan, in kasta oo ay culays ku yihiin shimbiraha, waxay abuuraan fursado daawasho shimbir oo cajiib ah.",
      "when_the_swallows_fly_high_the_weather": "“Haddii dab-shimbiraha kor u duulaan, cimiladu way qallalan doontaa. Haddii dab-shimbiraha hoos u duulaan, roob baa soo socda.” — Maahmaahdan dhaqameed dhab ahaantii si sayniska ah bay sax u tahay: cayayaanka (cuntada dab-shimbiraha) kor bay u duulaan nidaamyada cadaadis sare oo hoos bay u duulaan duufaanka ka hor.",
      "particle_color_guide": "🎨 Hagaha Midabka Qaybaha",
      "light_blue_slow_wind": " Buluug Khafiif ah = dabayl gaabis ah",
      "white_moderate_wind": " Caddaan = dabayl dhexdhexaad ah",
      "yellow_fast_wind": " Jaalle = dabayl dhaqso ah",
      "green_zone_upwash_rising_air": " Aagga Cagaaran = hawo-kor (hawo kor u kacaysa)",
      "red_zone_downwash_sinking_air": " Aagga Guduudan = hawo-hoos (hawo hoos u dhacaysa)",
      "delaware_bay": "Delaware Bay",
      "over_1_million_shorebirds_stop_here_to": "In ka badan 1 milyan oo shimbir xeebeed ayaa halkan ku joogsada si ay u cunaan ukunta carsaanyada faraska",
