      "when_do_birds_migrate": "📅 Goorma ayay Shimbiruhu Socdaalaan?",
      "migration_timing_varies_dramatically_b": "Waqtiga socdaalku si weyn buu u kala duwan yahay iyadoo ku xidhan noocyada:",
      "early_spring_waterfowl_ducks_geese_hea": "Gu' hore: Shimbiraha biyaha (bushimaha, baqooyinka) waxay u socdaan waqooyi iyagoo raacaya dhalaalka barafka. Red-winged Blackbirds waxay ku noqdaan dhul-qoyanka.",
      "peak_spring_warblers_vireos_tanagers_f": "Gu' sare: Warblers, vireos iyo tanagers waxay buuxiyaan waqooyiga. Shimbiraha heesa badankood habeen bay socdaalaan. Habeennada ugu sarreeya waxaa cirka jira in ka badan 500 milyan oo shimbir.",
      "shorebirds_start_south_some_species_fa": "Shimbiraha xeebeed waxay bilaabaan koonfur — noocyada qaar way ku “guuldareystaan” meelaha taranka waxayna bilaabaan inay soo noqdaan horraantii Luulyo. Waaweynku inta badan way baxaan ka hor ilmaha.",
      "peak_fall_raptors_ride_thermals_along_": "Dayr sare: Ugaadhsadayaashu waxay fuulaan qulqulka kulaylka silsiladaha buuraha. Shimbiraha heesa waxay u socdaan koonfur iyagoo raacaya wejiyada qabow. Baqooyinku waxay ku duulaan qaabka V habeenkii.",
      "photoperiod_day_length_is_the_primary_": "Muddada iftiinka (dhererka maalinta) waa kicinta koowaad ee socdaalka. Marka maalmuhu gaabtaan dayrta, hormoonnadu waxay kiciyaan “Zugunruhe” — degganaan-la'aanta socdaalka — shimbiruhuna waxay bilaabaan inay ururiyaan baruur (cunto-badan), mararka qaarkood iyagoo laba-labaynaya miisaanka jirka.",
      "stopover_ecology": "⛺ Deegaanka Goobaha Joogsiga",
      "stopovers_are_not_just_rest_stops_they": "Goobaha joogsigu maaha oo keliya goobo nasasho, waa ",
      "refueling_stations": "saldhigyada shidaal-buuxinta",
      "critical_to_survival_a_migrating_warbl": " oo muhiim u ah badbaadada. Warbler socdaal ah wuxuu ku qaadan karaa 75% waqtiga socdaalka goobaha joogsiga, isagoo si xoog leh u cunaya si uu dib ugu dhiso keydka baruurta. Deegaanka goobta joogsiga ee tayada leh wuxuu noqon karaa faraqa u dhexeeya nolol iyo dhimasho.",
      "at_delaware_bay_over_1_million_shorebi": "Delaware Bay, in ka badan 1 milyan oo shimbir xeebeed (Red Knots, Ruddy Turnstones, Sanderlings) waxay ku tiirsan yihiin ukunta carsaanyada faraska ee la dhigo Maajo. Waqtigu waa inuu saxsanaadaa: shimbiruhu waxay yimaadaan si sax ah waqtiga carsaanyada faraska ay ukunta dhigaan. Haddii tirada carsaanyada faraska hoos u dhacdo (sababtoo ah kalluumeysi xad-dhaaf ah oo dabiin), silsiladda socdaalka oo dhan way burburtaa.",
      "conservation_success_story_after_horse": "Sheeko guul ah oo ilaalin: Ka dib markii la soo bandhigay xadka goosashada carsaanyada faraska 2012, tirada Red Knot waxay bilowday inay si tartiib ah uga soo kabsato heerka ugu hooseeya ee qalalaasaha 15,000 ilaa in ka badan 50,000 marka la gaadho 2025.",
      "migration_physiology": "🦴 Fiisiyoolajiga Socdaalka",
      "migration_is_one_of_the_most_physicall": "Socdaalku waa mid ka mid ah hawlaha ugu jireed-culus boqortooyada xayawaanka. Shimbiruhu waxay maraan isbeddello jireed oo yaab leh ka hor inta aysan bixin:",
      "hyperphagia": "Cunto-badan",
      "before_migration_birds_enter_a_feeding": "Ka hor socdaalka, shimbiruhu waxay galaan cunto-badan oo la yiraahdo hyperphagia, iyagoo cunaya heer 2-3 jeer ka badan sida caadiga ah. Blackpoll Warbler (garaam 12) wuxuu ku daraa keyd baruur oo garaam 8-12 ah, isagoo ku dhawaad laba-labaynaya miisaanka jirka. Baruurtan waa shidaalka duulimaadyada aan istaag lahayn ee ka badan 2,000 mayl.",
      "organ_shrinkage": "Yaraanta Xubnaha",
      "to_reduce_weight_migrating_birds_actua": "Si ay u yareeyaan miisaanka, shimbiraha socdaalku waxay dhab ahaantii yareeyaan xubnaha dheefshiidka (xiidmaha, beerka, calaacasha) ilaa 40% ka hor inta aysan bixin. Marka ay gaadhaan goobaha joogsiga, waxay dib u dhisaan xubnahan si dhaqso ah si ay shidaal u buuxiyaan. “Beddelka phenotype-ka” tan waa mid gaar ah oo ka mid ah xayawaanka lafdhabarka leh.",
      "hemoglobin": "Hemoglobin",
      "high_altitude_migrants_like_bar_headed": "Socdaalayaasha dherer sare sida Bar-headed Geese (oo duula cag 29,000 oo ka sarreeya Himalaya) waxay leeyihiin hemoglobin gaar ah oo soo-jiidasho badan u leh ogsijiinta. Muruqyadooda waxay ka koobmaan myoglobin dheeraad ah, cufnaanta capillary-goodana waa laba jibbaar noocyada dhulka hooseeya.",
      "sleep_in_flight": "Hurdo Duulimaad Dhexdood ah",
      "some_birds_can_sleep_while_flying_usin": "Shimbiro qaar way seexan karaan iyagoo duulaya, iyagoo isticmaalaya “hurdo nus-maskaxeed” — iyagoo xiraya hal nus maskaxeed hal mar. Frigatebirds waxaa la duubay iyagoo seexanaya 42 daqiiqo maalintii inta lagu jiro duulimaadyada 10-maalmood ee badda ka gudbaya, iyagoo qaadanaya hurdo yaryar oo 12 ilbiriqsi ah mid kasta.",
      "navigation_clock": "Saacadda Hagitaanka",
      "birds_maintain_an_internal_circadian_c": "Shimbiruhu waxay ilaaliyaan saacad circadian gudaha ah oo sax badan oo la yaab leh. Saacaddan waxay magdhabtaa dhaqdhaqaaqa qorraxda cirka (buste qorrax oo waqti-magdhabis ah) waxayna la socotaa isbeddellada xilliyeed ee dhererka maalinta oo kicinaya hormoonnada socdaalka.",
      "zugunruhe": "Zugunruhe",
      "zugunruhe_migration_restlessness_is_a_": "Zugunruhe (“degganaan-la'aanta socdaalka”) waa xaalad dhaqan ah oo shimbiraha socdaalka ee lagu xidho qafis ay garabka ku ruxaan jihada ay dabiici ahaan u socdaali lahaayeen, waqtiga ay socdaali lahaayeen. Waa mid hormoon-kiciyo waxaana lagu keeydiyay hidde-side. Xataa shimbiraha gacanta lagu koriyay ee aan lahayn khibrad socdaal way muujiyaan Zugunruhe.",
      "species_comparison": "📊 Isbarbardhigga Noocyada",
