      "distances_are_approximate_annual_migra": "Masaafooyinku waa masaafooyin socdaal sannadeed oo qiyaasi ah. Xawaarahu waa xawaare safar caadi ah. Dhererku waa dherer socdaal caadi ah.",
      "how_scientists_track_migration": "📡 Sida Saynisyahannadu u Raadraacaan Socdaalka",
      "our_understanding_of_migration_has_bee": "Fahamkeenna socdaalka waxaa si weyn u beddelay tignoolajiyada:",
      "bird_banding": "Xidhitaanka Shimbir: ",
      "since_1920_over_80_million_birds_have_": "Ilaa 1920, in ka badan 80 milyan oo shimbir ayaa laga xidhay Waqooyiga Ameerika. Xarig kastaa wuxuu leeyahay nambar gaar ah. Marka shimbirka xidhan dib loo qabto, saynisyahannadu waxay wax ka bartaan badbaadada, waddooyinka iyo waqtiga. Heerka dib-u-helitaanku waa hooseeyaa (1-5%), laakiin xogtu aad bay u weyn tahay.",
      "gps_trackers": "Raadraacayaasha GPS: ",
      "solar_powered_gps_tags_now_as_small_as": "Calaamadaha GPS ee qorraxda ku shaqeeya (hadda oo yar sida garaam 1) waxay xogta goobta u soo diraan dayax-gacmeed. Waxay muujiyaan waddooyin sax ah, waqtiyada joogsiga iyo dhererka duulimaadka. Duulimaadka Godwit ee mayl 7,145 oo aan istaag lahayn waxaa lagu raadraacay GPS.",
      "light_level_geolocators_0_5g_record_su": "Geolocator-yada heer-iftiinka (garaam 0.5) waxay diiwaangeliyaan waqtiyada qorrax-soo-baxa iyo qorrax-dhaca. Marka shimbir dib loo qabto, saynisyahannadu waxay soo saaraan xogta waxayna xisaabiyaan latitude (dhererka maalinta) iyo longitude (waqtiga duhurka qorraxda). Saxnaanta: ~200 km.",
      "weather_radar": "Radaarka Cimilada: ",
      "nexrad_weather_radar_stations_across_t": "Saldhigyada radaarka cimilada ee NEXRAD ee Maraykanka oo dhan waxay ogaadaan raxammo waaweyn oo shimbiro socdaal ah. BirdCast (Cornell Lab) wuxuu isticmaalaa barashada mashiinka si uu u saadaaliyo oo u muujiyo socdaalka waqti-dhab ah xogta radaarka. Habeennada ugu sarreeya, radaarku wuxuu muujiyaa dhibco cagaaran oo waaweyn oo socdaal shimbir ah.",
      "citizen_scientists_submit_100_million_": "Saynisyahannada muwaadiniinta ah waxay gudbiyaan in ka badan 100 milyan oo indha-indhayn shimbir sannadkii iyagoo isticmaalaya eBird, iyagoo abuuraya kaydka xogta kala duwanaanshaha noolaha ee ugu weyn adduunka. Xogtan waxay muujisaa qaababka waqtiga iyo qaybinta socdaalka ee heer-qaarad ah oo aan koox cilmi-baaris ah oo keligeed ay ururin karin.",
      "motus_wildlife_tracking": "Raadraaca Duurjoogta Motus: ",
      "a_network_of_1_500_automated_radio_tel": "Shabakad ka kooban in ka badan 1,500 oo saldhig telemetry raadiyo tooska ah oo ka mid ah qaaradda Ameerika waxay ogaadaan shimbiraha calaamadaysan marka ay duulayaan. Saldhig kastaa wuxuu dhegeystaa mowjadaha raadiyaha gaarka ah, isagoo abuuraya shabakad ogaansho heer-qaarad ah. Shimbir calaamadaysan oo ka duulaya Canada ilaa Brazil waxaa ogaada dhawr saldhig oo waddada ah.",
