      "bernoulli_s_principle": "Mabda'a Bernoulli",
      "as_air_speeds_up_its_pressure_drops_a_": "Marka hawadu xawaare kordho, cadaadiskeedu wuu hoos u dhacaa. Dusha sare ee qalloocan ee garabku wuxuu ku qasbaa hawada inay si dhaqso ah u socoto korka marka loo eego hoosta. Tan waxay abuurtaa ",
      "lower_pressure_above": "cadaadis hooseeya korka",
