      "angle_of_attack_stall": "Xagasha Weerarka iyo Istaagga",
      "as_the_angle_of_attack_increases_lift_": "Marka xagasha weerarku kordho, kor-u-qaadku wuu kordhaa — ilaa meel. ",
      "critical_angle": "Xagasha muhiimka ah",
      "stall_angle_airflow_separates_from_the": " (xagasha istaagga) markii la dhaafo, socodka hawadu wuu ka go'aa dusha sare. Garabku wuu lumiyaa socodka hawada siman, kor-u-qaadku aad buu u dhacaa, jiiddana way boodaa. Kani waa “istaag”.",
      "current_wing_s_stall_angle": "Xagasha istaagga garabka hadda: ",
      "best_l_d_at": ". L/D ugu fiican: ",
      "lift_to_drag_ratio_l_d": "Saamiga Kor-u-qaad-ilaa-Jiid (L/D)",
      "l_d_measures_aerodynamic_efficiency_a_": "L/D wuxuu cabbiraa waxtarka aerodynamic. L/D sare wuxuu ka dhigan yahay kor-u-qaad badan halkii unug jiid. Albatrosku waxay gaadhaan saamiyada L/D ee heerka ",
      "meaning_20_pounds_of_lift_for_every_1_": " (taasoo ka dhigan 20 rodol oo kor-u-qaad ah halkii rodol 1 oo jiid ah), mid ka mid ah kuwa ugu fiican dabeecadda. Glider-yada casriga ah ",
      "induced_vs_parasite_drag": "Jiid Kicis ah vs Jiid Parasite",
      "induced_drag": "Jiid kicis ah",
      "is_a_byproduct_of_creating_lift_the_wi": " waa wax-soo-saar ka mid ah abuurista kor-u-qaadka: wareegyada cidhib-garab ee shimbiruhu isticmaalaan qaabka V. Wuu yaraadaa marka xawaare kordho. ",
      "parasite_drag": "Jiid parasite",
      "comes_from_the_bird_s_body_pushing_thr": " wuxuu ka yimaadaa jirka shimbirka oo hawada dhex riixaya; wuu kordhaa isku-dhufashada xawaaraha. Barta isgoyska ee labadan qalooc waxaa jira ",
      "minimum_drag_speed": "xawaaraha jiidda ugu hooseeya",
      "the_most_efficient_cruising_speed": " — xawaaraha safarka ugu waxtarka badan.",
      "reynolds_number": "Tirada Reynolds",
      "bird_flight_operates_at_reynolds_numbe": "Duulimaadka shimbirku wuxuu ku shaqeeyaa tirooyinka Reynolds inta u dhaxaysa 10,000 iyo 500,000 — nidaam aerodynamic adag. Cabbirradan lakabka xadka (lakab hawo khafiif ah oo ku dhegan dusha garabka) waa qayb laminar, qayb qallafsan. Baalasha shimbiruhu waxay abuuraan qallafsanaan-yar oo dhab ahaantii ",
      "maintain_airflow_attachment_especially": " ilaalisa ku-xidhnaanta socodka hawada, gaar ahaan xagasha weerar ee waaweyn. Kani waa wax injineerradu ay wali isku dayayaan inay ku soo celiyaan naqshadaha drone-ka.",
      "bio_inspired_engineering": "⚙️ Injineerinka Bayooloji-dhiirriga leh",
      "bird_flight_has_inspired_countless_eng": "Duulimaadka shimbirku wuxuu dhiirrigeliyay hal-abuurro injineerin oo aan la tirin karin:",
      "winglets": "Winglets",
      "the_upturned_wingtips_on_modern_airlin": "Cidhib-garabyada kor loo rogay ee dayuuradaha rakaabka casriga ah (Boeing 737 MAX, Airbus A350) waxaa si toos ah looga dhiirrigeliyay baalasha cidhib-kala qaybsan ee gorgorrada. “Winglets”-yadan waxay yareeyaan jiidda kicinta 5-7%, iyagoo shirkadaha duulimaadka u badbaadinaya balaayiin kharash shidaal ah sannadkii. Waxay u shaqeeyaan iyagoo jebinaya wareega cidhib-garabka.",
      "owl_quiet_fans": "Marwaxadaha Aamusan sida Gumburaha",
      "owl_feathers_have_a_serrated_leading_e": "Baalasha gumburu waxay leeyihiin cidhib hore oo ilko leh, qaab dusha oo velvet u eg, iyo cidhib dambe oo firaaqo leh, kuwaas oo wada yareeya buuq aerodynamic ilaa ku dhawaad aamusnaan. Injineerrada GE iyo Dyson waxay ku dayday sifooyinkan baalasha turbine-ka iyo naqshadaha marwaxadda, iyagoo yareeya buuqa in ka badan 10 decibel.",
      "kingfisher_bullet_trains": "Tareennada Xabbadaha ah ee Kingfisher-ka Dhiirrigeliyay",
      "the_shinkansen_bullet_train_s_nose_was": "Sanka tareenka xabbadda ah ee Shinkansen waxaa dib loo naqshadeeyay ka dib markii injineer daawadaha shimbiraha Eiji Nakatsu uu arkay kingfishers oo ka quusaya hawada una gala biyaha iyagoon biyo kicin. Sanka qaabka afka kingfisher-ka leh wuxuu yareeyay qarxinta dhawaaqa 30% iyo isticmaalka korontada 15% marka tareenku ka soo baxo tunnellada.",
      "morphing_wings": "Garabbada Qaab-beddelaya",
      "birds_continuously_adjust_wing_shape_a": "Shimbiruhu si joogto ah bay u hagaajiyaan qaabka garabka, xagasha iyo booska baalka inta lagu jiro duulimaadka — si casri ah oo ka badan dayuurad kasta. NASA iyo MIT waxay horumarinayaan tignoolajiyada “garab qaab-beddelaya” oo isticmaasha walxo dabacsan iyo actuator-yo si ay ugu daydaan hagaajinta garabka shimbirka, iyagoo suurtogal ah inay hagaajiyaan waxtarka 8-12%.",
      "feather_engineering": "🪶 Injineerinka Baalka",
      "a_bird_feather_is_one_of_the_most_comp": "Baalka shimbirku waa mid ka mid ah qaababka ugu adag dabeecadda. Baal duulimaad wuxuu leeyahay:",
      "the_central_shaft_a_hollow_tube_strong": "Ulaha dhexe — tuubbo godan, oo ka xoog badan bir saamiga miisaanka, oo laga sameeyay beta-keratin.",
      "hundreds_of_branches_growing_from_the_": "Boqollaal laamo oo ka soo baxa ulaha, iyagoo sameeya baalka.",
      "tiny_hook_like_structures_connecting_b": "Qaabab yaryar oo qabsato u eg oo isku xidha laamaha sida velcro. Baal qoolley ah wuxuu leeyahay qiyaastii 1 milyan qabsato yaryar.",
      "microscopic_hooks_on_barbules_that_zip": "Qabsatooyin microscopic ah oo ku yaal barbules-ka oo isku xidha laamaha sida zip, iyagoo sameeya dusha aan hawada gelin. Marka baalku kala firdho, shimbirku wuxuu afkiisa ku shanleyn karaa oo dib u “zip” gareyn karaa.",
      "flight_feathers_are_asymmetric_the_lea": "Baalasha duulimaadku ma sinna — baalka cidhibta hore wuu ka dhuuban yahay cidhibta dambe. Sinnaan-la'aantan waxay abuurtaa qaabka airfoil qalloocan oo dhaliya kor-u-qaad, sida garabka dayuuradda. Baalasha aasaasiga ah ee cidhib-garabyada waxay maroojiyaan inta lagu jiro garaaca-hoose, iyagoo u shaqeeya sida baalasha propeller-ka gaarka ah.",
      "birds_have_1_000_25_000_feathers_a_swa": "Shimbiruhu waxay leeyihiin 1,000 ilaa 25,000 baal (swan-ka ayaa ugu badan). Waxay beddelaan dhammaan baalashooda duulimaadka sannad kasta inta lagu jiro ",
      "typically_after_breeding_season_and_be": ", inta badan xilliga taranka ka dib iyo socdaalka ka hor. Luminta baalal badan hal mar waxay ka dhigi kartaa shimbir mid aan duuli karin, sidaas darteed baal-ridku wuxuu raacaa isku-mid-ahaansho dhinac-labeed sax ah: baalasha u dhigma ee garab kasta waxaa la beddelaa hal mar.",
      "migration_energy_budget": "⚡ Miisaaniyadda Tamarta Socdaalka",
