      "margin_of_safety_2_kcal_11": "Xadka badbaadada: ~2 kcal (11%)",
      "that_is_an_incredibly_thin_margin_a_st": "Kaasi waa xad khafiif ah oo la yaab leh. Dabayl hore oo xoog leh, weji qabow, ama gaadhista xeebta oo leh miisaan-yari 10% ah waxay noqon kartaa dhimasho. Taasi waa sababta tayada deegaanka goobta joogsiga ay tahay ",
      "literally_life_or_death": "arrin nolol ama dhimasho ah dhab ahaan",
