      "guide_a_flock_of_canada_geese_from_the": "Hag raxan Canada Geese ah oo ka socda meelaha taranka ee waqooyiga Canada ilaa deegaannada jiilaalka ee Koonfurta Ameerika. Go'aammo ka gaadho cimilada, goobaha nasashada iyo waddooyinka. Ma keeni kartaa raxanta guriga si nabad ah?",
