      "migratory_birds_face_growing_dangers_u": "Shimbiraha socdaalka waxay wajahaan khataro sii kordhaya. Fahamka khataradan waa tallaabada koowaad ee ilaalinta.",
      "what_you_can_do": "🌱 Waxaad Samayn Karto",
      "lights_out": "Dami Nalalka: ",
      "turn_off_unnecessary_lights_during_spr": "Dami nalalka aan loo baahnayn inta lagu jiro socdaalka gu'ga iyo dayrta (Maarso-Maajo, Ogosto-Nofeembar). Xataa dhismo hal ah oo mugdi ah wuxuu badbaadin karaa boqollaal shimbir habeenkii.",
      "window_decals": "Astaamaha Daaqadaha: ",
      "apply_bird_safe_decals_to_windows_bird": "Ku dhaji astaamo shimbir-badbaadis ah daaqadaha. Shimbiruhu waxay ku arkaan muraayadda milicsiga cirka iyo geedaha, ma aha muraayadda lafteeda. Astaamaha la dhigo kala fogaan cm 5 waxay jebiyaan milicsiga.",
      "native_plants": "Dhirta Asalka ah: ",
      "plant_native_trees_and_shrubs_that_pro": "Beero geedo iyo geedo yaryar oo asal ah oo soo saara midho oo soo jiita cayayaanka — shidaal muhiim ah shimbiraha socdaalka. Dhirta aan asalka ahayn inta badan ma laha cayayaanka shimbiruhu u baahan yihiin.",
      "keep_cats_inside": "Ku Hay Bisadaha Gudaha: ",
      "indoor_cats_live_longer_healthier_live": "Bisadaha guriga waxay nool yihiin nolol dheer, caafimaad qabta oo badbaadiyaan shimbiraha. Qof walba wuu guuleystaa.",
      "citizen_science": "Sayniska Muwaadinka: ",
      "use_apps_like_ebird_cornell_lab_to_rep": "Isticmaal abbaarooyinka sida eBird (Cornell Lab) si aad uga warbixiso indha-indhaynta shimbiraha. Xogtaadu waxay ka caawisaa saynisyahannada inay raadraacaan waqtiga socdaalka iyo isbeddellada tirada.",
      "support_habitat": "Taageer Deegaanka: ",
      "advocate_for_wetland_protection_and_re": "U doodo ilaalinta dhul-qoyanka iyo dhigista tamarta dabaysha oo mas'uul ah bulshadaada.",
      "did_you_know": "🤔 Ma Ogtahay?",
      "on_peak_migration_nights": "Habeennada socdaalka ugu sarreeya ",
      "over_500_million_birds": "in ka badan 500 milyan oo shimbir",
      "are_in_the_air_over_north_america_simu": " ayaa cirka ku jira Waqooyiga Ameerika hal mar. Saldhigyada radaarka cimilada waxay ogaadaan daruuro waaweyn oo shimbiro socdaal ah oo duulaya qorrax-dhaca. Waxaad daawan kartaa socdaalka waqti-dhab ah BirdCast (birdcast.info).",
      "most_songbird_migration_happens_at_nig": "Socdaalka shimbiraha heesa badankiisu wuxuu dhacaa habeenkii, marka hawadu deggan tahay, ugaadhsadayaashu yar yihiin, xiddiguhuna u muuqdaan hagitaanka. Shimbiruhu waxay isticmaalaan ",
      "setting_sun": "qorrax-dhaca",
      "to_calibrate_their_star_compass_at_dus": " si ay ku toosiyaan buskiga xiddigahooda fiidkii.",
      "magnetic_sense": "Dareenka magnetic-ka",
      "of_birds_may_work_through_quantum_mech": " ee shimbiraha wuxuu u shaqeyn karaa iyada oo loo marayo quantum mechanics. Borotiinnada cryptochrome ee ku jira indhaha shimbiraha waxay isticmaali karaan isku-xidhka quantum si ay u ogaadaan aagga magnetic-ka Dhulka — iyagoo ka dhigaya hagitaanka shimbiraha mid ka mid ah hababka bayoolaji ee yar ee ku tiirsan fiisigiska quantum.",
      "some_bird_species_can_detect_the": "Noocyada shimbiraha qaar waxay ogaan karaan ",
      "polarization_pattern": "qaabka polarization",
      "of_sunlight_even_through_heavy_cloud_c": " ee iftiinka qorraxda xataa daruuro culus dhexdood, iyagoo isticmaalaya cones gaar ah oo UV-dareen ah oo ku jira retina-goodda. Tan waxay ka dhigan tahay xataa maalmaha daruuraha leh shimbiruhu waxay go'aamin karaan booska qorraxda oo ay ilaaliyaan waddadooda.",
      "the_brain_s_memory_center_is_significa": " (xarunta xusuusta maskaxda) aad bay uga weyn tahay noocyada shimbiraha socdaalka marka loo eego noocyada aan socdaalin. Dhab ahaantii way korodhaa inta lagu jiro xilliga socdaalka, iyadoo ku darsata neurons cusub oo geedi socod la yiraahdo neurogenesis qaangaar ah. Way dib u yaraataa socdaalka ka dib. Beddelka xilliyeed ee maskaxda tan waa aag muhiim ah oo cilmiga neurosayniska ah.",
      "migration_vocabulary": "📖 Ereyada Socdaalka",
      "back_to_stem_lab_tool_list": "Ku noqo liiska qalabka STEM Lab",
      "back": "Dib",
      "migration_wind_lab_sections": "Qaybaha Shaybaadhka Socdaalka iyo Dabaysha",
      "fatal": "Dilaa",
      "energy_budget_50_of_distance_bird_woul": "Miisaaniyadda tamarta < 50% masaafada — shimbirku wuxuu ku dhiman lahaa gaajo badhtamaha jidka. Joogsigu waa qasab.",
      "borderline": "Xadka",
      "energy_budget_near_distance_possible_w": "Miisaaniyadda tamarta u dhow masaafada — suurtogal ah dabayl dambe oo kaamil ah, haddii kalese joogsiyadu waa qasab.",
      "feasible": "Suurtogal",
      "single_leg_flight_realistic_but_tight_": "Duulimaad hal-lug ah waa mid dhab ah laakiin cidhiidhi. Noocyada badankood way shidaal-buuxiyaan badhtamaha jidka si kastaba.",
      "comfortable": "Raaxo leh",
      "distance_is_well_within_energy_budget_": "Masaafadu si fiican bay ugu jirtaa miisaaniyadda tamarta. Adkeysiga heerka Bar-tailed Godwit.",
      "easy": "Fudud",
      "3_reserve_either_short_distance_or_ove": "Keyd 3× ama ka badan. Ama masaafo gaaban ama keyd baruur dheeraad ah.",
      "energy_inquiry_can_the_bird_make_it": "🔬 Baaritaanka Tamarta — Shimbirku Ma Gaari Karaa?",
      "pick_wingspan_mass_headwind_formation_": "Dooro ballaca garabka, cufka, dabaysha hore, qaabka iyo masaafada. Saadaali xaaladda tamarta. Dhibco ma jiraan, muujin ma jirto.",
