      "your_hypothesis_which_parameter_forces": "Mala-awaalkaaga (parameter-kee ayaa qasba joogsiyada ugu badan?)",
      "e_g_v_formation_savings_only_pay_off_a": "tusaale ahaan Badbaadinta qaabka V waxay faa'iido bixisaa kaliya ka sarreeya km 1,500, sababtoo ah kharashka duulimaadku wuu xukumaa...",
      "i_m_stuck_show_open_questions": "🤔 Waan istaagay — Muuji su'aalaha furan",
      "open_questions_no_answer_key": "Su'aalaha furan (ma jiro furaha jawaabta)",
      "why_would_a_heavier_bird_necessarily_n": "Maxay shimbir culus ugu baahan lahaa tamar dheeraad ah km kasta — sidee tani ula xiriirtaa jiidda?",
      "a_10_m_s_headwind_doubles_the_work_wha": "Dabayl hore oo 10 m/s ah waxay laba-labaysaa shaqada — maxaa dhici doona haddii badhka safarku uu leeyahay dabayl dambe oo 10 m/s ah?",
      "why_is_v_formation_savings_about_22_wh": "Maxay badbaadinta qaabka V u tahay qiyaastii 22%? Immisa ayay ku kacdaa shimbirta hoggaaminaysa?",
      "how_does_a_hummingbird_4_g_1500_km_gul": "Sidee hummingbird (garaam 4, gudbitaanka Gulf of Mexico km 1,500) uga badbaadaa socdaalkiisa?",
      "i_can_explain_why_this_profile_yields_": "Waan sharraxi karaa sababta profile-kani u dhaliyo xaaladdan tamarta.",
      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Ku sharrax ereyadaada gaarka ah...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Widget baaritaan — dhibco ma jiraan, muujin ma jirto, daad jawaab ma jiro. Moodelka tamartu waa tusaale (jiid ∝ m^0.67 / ballaca garabka). Badbaadinta qaabka V way kala duwan tahay ~10 ilaa 30% iyadoo ku xidhan nooca iyo booska (Lissaman & Shollenberger 1970, xadka sare ee aragtiyeed; cabbirrada duulimaadka dhexdiisa waxaa ka mid ah Weimerskirch et al. 2001 oo ku saabsan pelican iyo Portugal et al. 2014 oo ku saabsan ibis). Widget-ku wuxuu isticmaalaa 22% qiyaas dhexdhexaad ah. Deegaanka dhabta ah ee goobaha joogsiga, fiiri suugaanta aasaasiga ah.",
      "v_formation_flying": "Duulimaadka Qaabka V",
      "trailing_birds_catch_the_upwash_from_t": "Shimbiraha dambe waxay qabtaan hawo-korka shimbirta hore — badbaadin tamar 20-30%. Booska hoggaanku wuu wareegaa sababtoo ah shimbirta hore ayaa shaqada ugu badan qabata.",
      "wind_currents_thermals": "Qulqulka Dabaysha + Qulqulka Kulaylka",
      "birds_read_pressure_gradients_we_canno": "Shimbiruhu waxay akhriyaan gradient-yada cadaadiska aynaan dareemi karin. Hawo-korka, qulqulka tiirka iyo tiirarka kulaylku waa waddada ay ugaadhsadayaashu ku duulaan boqollaal mayl iyagoo gubaya ku dhawaad kalori eber.",
      "migration_routes_flyways": "Waddooyinka Socdaalka + Waddooyinka Duulimaadka",
      "four_major_north_american_flyways_paci": "Afarta waddo-duulimaad ee waaweyn ee Waqooyiga Ameerika (Pacific, Dhexe, Mississippi, Atlantic) waxay hagaan balaayiin shimbiro laba jeer sannadkii. Maine waxay ku taal xagga sare ee waddo-duulimaadka Atlantic.",
      "aerodynamics_of_bird_flight": "Cilmiga Dhaqdhaqaaqa Hawada ee Duulimaadka Shimbirka",
      "wing_shape_aspect_ratio_camber_tunes_l": "Qaabka garabka (saamiga muuqaalka + qalloocdo) wuxuu hagaajiyaa kor-u-qaadka marka loo eego jiidda. Shimbiraha duula = saami muuqaal sare, garaac garab gaabis ah. Hummingbird = saami muuqaal hooseeya, garaac garab ka badan 60 Hz.",
      "weather_navigation": "Cimilo + Hagitaan",
      "birds_use_multiple_cues_simultaneously": "Shimbiruhu waxay isticmaalaan tilmaamo badan hal mar — buste qorrax, aagga magnetic-ka iyada oo loo marayo cryptochrome isha ku jira, qaababka xiddigaha iyo calaamadaha dhulka ee la bartay. Way adkeysanayaan luminta tilmaan kasta oo keliya.",
      "v_formation_wind_currents_flyways_aero": "Qaabka V • Qulqulka Dabaysha • Waddooyinka Duulimaadka • Cilmiga Dhaqdhaqaaqa Hawada • Hagitaan"
