      "hero_ppm": "CO₂ maanta: ~424 ppm — kan ugu sarreeya in ka badan 3 milyan sannadood",
      "climate_mission": "Hawsha cimilada",
      "climate_explorer": "Climate Explorer",
      "mission_panel_copy": "U guur xogta shakhsiga una guur caddaymo caalami ah, caddaalad, iyo xalal. Sheybaarada siyaasadda iyo riixista horumarsan way sii jiraan marka aad ballaadhiso.",
