      "carbon_calculator_2": "Xisaabiyaha Kaarboonka",
      "average_us_household_emits_16_tons_co_": "Qoyska celceliska Maraykanka wuxuu sii daayaa ~16 tan CO₂/sannad. Wax-kicinta ugu waaweyn waa kuleylinta guriga, gaadiidka, iyo cunto-nolosha — ma aha caagagga plastikada.",
      "renewable_energy": "Tamar la cusboonaysiin karo",
      "solar_wind_are_now_cheaper_than_new_fo": "Qorrax + dabayl ayaa hadda ka jaban warshadaha fosil ee cusub suuqyada intooda badan. Qaybta adag waa isku-darka shabakadda, ma aha kharashka wax-soo-saarka.",
      "the_keeling_curve": "Qalooca Keeling",
      "continuous_co_measurement_at_mauna_loa": "Cabbir joogto ah oo CO₂ ah Mauna Loa tan iyo 1958 — diiwaanka jawiga ugu socda muddada dheer. Qaabka ilkaha miinshaarka wuxuu ka yimaadaa photosynthesis-ka Waqooyiga Adduunka.",
      "climate_tipping_points": "Bartaha isbeddelka cimilada",
      "thresholds_where_the_system_shifts_sta": "Xadadka halka nidaamku uu ka beddelo xaalad oo uu halkaas ku sii jiro — dhalaalka Greenland, hoos u dhaca Amazon, gaabinta AMOC. Shaqada dhawaan ayaa soo jeedinaysa in dhowr ay u dhowaan yihiin ka intii la moodayay.",
      "climate_justice_2": "Caddaaladda cimilada",
      "the_countries_that_emitted_the_least_f": "Dalalka ugu qiiqa yar soo saaray ayaa la kulmaya saameynta ugu daran. Cimiladu waa arrin sinnaan marka hore — nuglaanshuhu wuxuu raacaa dakhliga, juqraafiga, iyo mas'uuliyadda taariikhiga ah.",
      "solutions_toolkit": "Qalabka Xalka",
      "drawdown_ranks_100_solutions_by_gigato": "Drawdown wuxuu kala saaraa 100 xal gigatons CO₂ ee laga fogaaday. Qaboojiyaha, khasaaraha cuntada, iyo waxbarashada gabdhaha ayaa liiska ugu sarreeya — ma aha waxa dadka badankiisu maleeyaan.",
