      "e_g_mitosis_has_four_main_phases_proph": "Tusaale \"Mitosis waxay leedahay afar wejiyada ugu waaweyn: prophase, metaphase, [[telophase]], iyo anaphase. Inta lagu jiro metaphase chromosomes waxay ku safan yihiin [[xariiqda xuubka nukleeska]] ka hor inta aysan kala go'in.\"",
