      "206_bones_support_protection_movement_": "Lafo 206 — taageero, ilaalin, dhaqdhaqaaq, kaydinta macdanta, samaynta dhiigga.",
      "houses_meninges_brain_and_cranial_nerv": "Waxay ka koobantahay meninges, maskax, iyo daloolada dareemayaasha madaxa. Tolmooyinka (coronal, sagittal, lambdoid) way isku dhegaan markuu ilmuhu gaaro 2 sano.",
