      "pelvic_floor_levator_ani": "Sagxadda Miskaha (Levator Ani)",
      "diaphragm_muscle": "Diaphragm (Muruq)",
      "heart_60_000_miles_of_vessels_5l_of_bl": "Wadne, 60,000 mayl oo xididdo ah, 5L dhiig ah — wuxuu gudbiyaa O₂, nafaqooyin, hormoonno; wuxuu saaraa qashinka.",
      "circle_of_willis": "Circle of Willis",
      "great_saphenous_vein": "Xididka Weyn ee Saphenous",
      "lymphatic_vessels": "Xididada Lymph",
      "cns_brain_spinal_cord_and_pns_31_spina": "CNS (maskax + laf-dhabar) iyo PNS (31 lammaane oo dareemayaal dhabar ah, 12 lammaane oo dareemayaal madax ah, nidaamka dareemaha is-maamula).",
      "lightest_sleep_transition_from_wakeful": "Hurdada ugu fudud — kala-guur ka soo baxa toosnaanta. Dhaqdhaqaaq indho oo tartiib ah, xoogga muruqa oo yaraanaya. Gariirka hypnic (dhaqdhaqaaqa myoclonic) waa caadi. Si fudud loo toosiyo. Mowjadaha vertex ee fiiqan waxay ka soo muuqdaan EEG.",
      "true_sleep_begins_core_body_temperatur": "Hurdo dhab ah ayaa bilaabmaysa. Heerkulka gudaha jirka wuu hoos u dhacaa, garaaca wadnaha wuu gaabiyaa. Sleep spindles (qaraxyada thalamocortical) waxay ilaaliyaan hurdada waxayna xoojiyaan xusuusta dhaqdhaqaaqa. K-complexes waa mowjado waaweyn oo ka jawaabaya kicinta dibadda.",
      "deep_slow_wave_sleep_sws_most_restorat": "Hurdo qoto dheer/mowjad gaaban (SWS). Marxaladda ugu soo celisa. Sii-deynta hormoonka koritaanka way gaartaa heerka ugu sarreeya. Nidaamka glymphatic wuxuu nadiifiyaa qashinka maskaxda (amyloid-β). Xoojinta xusuusta caddaynta ayaa dhacda. Ugu adag in la toosiyo; miyir-beel hurdo haddii la toosiyo.",
      "dreaming_stage_brain_is_highly_active_": "Marxaladda riyada. Maskaxdu aad bay u firfircoon tahay (sida toosnaanta) laakiin jirku wuu curyaamaa (atonia iyada oo maskax-jirridu joojinayso dareemayaasha dhaqdhaqaaqa). Dhaqdhaqaaq indho oo degdeg ah oo isku-dubbariday. Farsamaynta xusuusta shucuurta iyo xallinta dhibaatada hal-abuurka. Wareegyadu way sii dheeraadaan habeenka intuu socdo.",
      "cerebral_cortex_4_lobes": "Cortex-ka Maskaxda (4 Lobe)",
      "brodmann_areas_map_52_cytoarchitectura": "Aagagga Brodmann waxay khariidad u sameeyaan 52 aag oo qaab-unug ah. Cortex-ka dhaqdhaqaaqa aasaasiga ah (aag 4), cortex-ka dareenka jirka aasaasiga ah (aag 3,1,2), cortex-ka aragga aasaasiga ah (aag 17), cortex-ka maqalka aasaasiga ah (aag 41,42). Cortex-ka prefrontal ayaa ugu dambeeya myelin (~25 sano).",
      "purkinje_cells_are_among_the_largest_n": "Unugyada Purkinje waa mid ka mid ah dareemayaasha ugu waaweyn, mid kastaa wuxuu helaa qiyaastii 200,000 gelin synaptic ah. Cortex-ka cerebellar wuxuu leeyahay 3 lakab: molecular, Purkinje, granular. Cilmi-baaris cusub waxay muujinaysaa doorkiisa garashada, shucuurta, iyo luqadda.",
      "brainstem_midbrain_pons_medulla": "Maskax-jirridka (Maskaxda Dhexe, Pons, Medulla)",
      "contains_nuclei_for_cranial_nerves_iii": "Wuxuu ka koobanyahay nuclei dareemayaasha madaxa III–XII. Nidaamka reticular activating (RAS) waa \"furaha shidaya\" maskaxda — dhaawac wuxuu keenaa suuxdin. Isgoyska piramidka medulla: isgoyska dhaqdhaqaaqa wuxuu sharraxayaa xakamaynta dhaqdhaqaaqa dhinaca ka soo horjeeda.",
      "memory_replay_during_sleep_hippocampal": "Dib-u-ciyaarinta xusuusta inta lagu jiro hurdada: dareemayaasha hippocampal waxay \"dib u ciyaaraan\" waaya-aragnimadii maalinta inta lagu jiro hurdada N3, iyagoo u wareejinaya xusuusaha neocortex. Unugyada grid ee cortex-ka entorhinal waxay siiyaan unugyada meel ee hippocampal iskuxidhka meelaha.",
      "fear_conditioning_pathway_auditory_cor": "Waddada barashada cabsida: cortex-ka maqalka → amygdala dhinaca → amygdala dhexe → hypothalamus (jawaab walwal) + PAG (barafowga). Isdhexgalka amygdala-prefrontal wuxuu ogolaadaa xakamaynta shucuurta — aasaaska daaweynta CBT.",
      "key_nuclei_vpl_vpm_somatosensory_relay": "Nuclei muhiim ah: VPL/VPM (gudbinta dareenka jirka), LGN (gudbinta aragga V1), MGN (gudbinta maqalka A1), pulvinar (feejignaan), kooxda nuclei hore (xusuus, wareegga Papez).",
      "thermostat_analogy_anterior_hypothalam": "Tusaalaha thermostat: hypothalamus hore wuxuu kiciyaa qaboojin (ballaarinta xididada, dhidid); hypothalamus dambe wuxuu kiciyaa kululayn (gariir, cidhiidhinta xididada). Qandho = heer sare oo prostaglandins ka soo baxa caabuqa.",
      "split_brain_experiments_revealed_hemis": "Tijaabooyinka maskax-kala-qaybinta waxay muujiyeen takhasus-gaarka barkinka: barkinka bidix = luqad, macquul; barkinka midig = farsamaynta meelaha, guud. Macluumaadka la siiyo hal goob-aragti waxaa farsameeya barkinka dhinaca ka soo horjeeda.",
      "dopamine_from_substantia_nigra_modulat": "Dopamine ka yimaada substantia nigra wuxuu maamulaa waddooyinka tooska ah (D1, kicinaya) iyo kuwa aan tooska ahayn (D2, joojinaya). Luminta maamulkan Parkinson wuxuu keenaa dhibaato gaar ah oo bilaabista dhaqdhaqaaqa.",
      "cranial_nerves_i_xii": "Dareemayaasha Madaxa (I-XII)",
      "returns_interstitial_fluid_absorbs_die": "Wuxuu soo celiyaa dareeraha unugyada dhexdooda, wuxuu nuugaa dufanka cuntada, ilaalinta difaaca — 600–700 qanjidh lymph, thymus, beeryaro.",
      "major_visceral_organs_respiration_dige": "Xubnaha waaweyn ee gudaha — neefsasho, dheefshiid, sifayn, xakamaynta endocrine.",
