      "the_circulatory_system_delivers_deoxyg": "Nidaamka wareegga dhiigga wuxuu gaarsiiyaa dhiigga aan lahayn oksijiin sambabbada, halkaas oo nidaamka neefsashadu ku buuxiyo oksijiin oo saaro carbon dioxide iyada oo loo maro xuubka khafiifka ah ee alveoli-capillary.",
      "neuromuscular_junction": "Isgoyska Dareen-Muruq",
      "motor_neurons_from_the_nervous_system_": "Dareemayaasha dhaqdhaqaaqa ee nidaamka dareemaha waxay sii daayaan acetylcholine isgoyska dareen-muruqa, iyagoo kiciya foosha fiilada muruqa. Iyada oo aan la helin calaamado dareemeed, muruqyadu ma dhaqaaqi karaan.",
      "lever_system_for_movement": "Nidaamka Lever ee Dhaqdhaqaaqa",
      "muscles_attach_to_bones_via_tendons_an": "Muruqyadu waxay ku dhegaan lafaha iyaga oo maraya seedaha waxayna jiidaan xubnaha isku-xirka, iyagoo abuuraya nidaamyada lever. Qalfoofku wuxuu bixiyaa lever adag; muruqyadu waxay bixiyaan xoogga jiidista.",
      "hormonal_regulation_of_reproduction": "Xakamaynta Hormoonka ee Taranka",
      "the_hypothalamus_pituitary_axis_releas": "Axis hypothalamus-pituitary wuxuu sii daayaa FSH iyo LH kuwaas oo xakameeya qanjidhada taranka. Estrogen, progesterone, iyo testosterone ee ka yimaada xubnaha taranka waxay jawaab u celiyaan nidaamka endocrine.",
      "immune_defense_and_fluid_balance": "Difaaca Difaaca iyo Isku-dheellitirka Dareeraha",
      "the_lymphatic_system_returns_interstit": "Nidaamka lymph wuxuu soo celiyaa dareeraha unugyada dhexdooda wareegga dhiigga wuxuuna geeyaa unugyada difaaca ee laga sameeyo xubnaha lymph. Labada nidaamba waxay ilaaliyaan homeostasis dareeraha waxayna la dagaallamaan caabuqa.",
      "hypothalamic_pituitary_axis_2": "Axis Hypothalamic-Pituitary",
      "the_hypothalamus_bridges_the_nervous_a": "Hypothalamus wuxuu isku xiraa nidaamyada dareemaha iyo endocrine — wuxuu isku daraa calaamadaha dareemaha wuxuuna u tarjumaa amarro hormoon oo xakameeya qanjidhka pituitary iyo dhammaan silsiladaha hormoonka ee ka hooseeya.",
      "breathing_mechanics": "Farsamada Neefsashada",
      "the_diaphragm_and_intercostal_muscles_": "Diaphragm iyo muruqyada feedhaha dhexdooda waxay si jireed u ballaariyaan oo u cidhiidhiyaan godka laabta si ay hawada u dhaqaajiyaan. Sambabbadu iyagu muruq ma laha waxayna gebi ahaanba ku tiirsan yihiin muruqyada ku hareeraysan.",
      "sensory_receptors_in_skin": "Qaataha Dareenka ee Maqaarka",
      "the_skin_contains_millions_of_speciali": "Maqaarka wuxuu ka koobanyahay malaayiin dhammaad dareemeyaal gaar ah iyo qaataha xiran oo dareema taabasho, cadaadis, heerkul, iyo xanuun, iyagoo si joogto ah u siiya nidaamka dareemaha xog dareen.",
      "portal_circulation_and_nutrient_proces": "Wareegga Portal iyo Farsamaynta Nafaqada",
      "blood_from_the_gi_tract_drains_through": "Dhiigga ka yimaada mareenka GI wuxuu ku dareeraa xididka hepatic portal si toos ah beerka ka hor inta uusan galin wareegga guud, taasoo u ogolaanaysa beerka inuu marka hore farsameeyo nafaqada oo uu saaro sunta.",
      "bone_marrow_blood_cell_production": "Samaynta Unugyada Dhiigga ee Dhuuxa Lafta",
      "red_bone_marrow_inside_the_skeleton_is": "Dhuuxa lafta cas ee ku dhex jira qalfoofku waa goobta ay ka dhashaan dhammaan unugyada dhiigga. Unugyada dhiigga cas, unugyada dhiigga cad, iyo platelets dhammaantood halkan ayaa laga sameeyaa iyada oo loo maro samaynta dhiigga.",
