      "the_runner_s_knee": "Jilibka Orodyahanka",
      "which_structure_is_most_likely_affecte": "Qaab-dhismeedkee ayaa ugu badan inuu saameeyo?",
      "patella_patellofemoral_joint": "Xarragada jilibka / xubinta patellofemoral",
      "patellofemoral_pain_syndrome_occurs_wh": "Cudurka xanuunka patellofemoral wuxuu dhacaa marka xarragada jilibku aanay si fiican ugu dhaqaaqin dooxadeeda femurka. Cadaadis soo noqnoqda oo orodka ka yimaada wuxuu keenaa xanaaq cartilage. Daaweyntu waxay ka kooban tahay xoojinta quad, xasilinta miskaha, iyo beddelka waxqabadka.",
      "the_shoulder_that_won_t_lift": "Garabka Aan Kicin",
      "which_structure_is_most_likely_torn": "Qaab-dhismeedkee ayaa ugu badan inuu jeexmo?",
      "supraspinatus_tendon_rotator_cuff": "Seedda supraspinatus (rotator cuff)",
      "the_supraspinatus_is_the_most_commonly": "Supraspinatus waa muruqa rotator cuff ee ugu badan jeexmada. Wuxuu maraa acromion hoostiisa halkaas oo uu la kulmo cadaadis iyo jeexitaan. Shaqada madaxa korkiisa sida rinjiyaynta ayaa si weyn u kordhisa khatartan.",
      "racing_heart_after_exercise": "Wadne Degdeg u Garaacaya Jimicsiga Kadib",
      "which_structure_controls_the_normal_he": "Qaab-dhismeedkee ayaa xakameeya garaaca wadnaha caadiga ah?",
      "sinoatrial_sa_node": "Sinoatrial (SA) node",
      "the_sa_node_in_the_right_atrium_is_the": "SA node ee atrium-ka midig waa pacemaker dabiiciga ah ee wadnaha. Inta lagu jiro jimicsi daran, adrenaline wuxuu keeni karaa garaac aan waxyeello lahayn markuu garaaca wadnuhu hagaajinayo. Arrhythmias sii socda waa in la baaro si looga saaro cudurka wadnaha ee qaab-dhismeedka.",
      "the_numb_hand": "Gacanta Xasillan",
      "which_nerve_is_being_compressed": "Dareemahee ayaa la cadaadinayaa?",
      "median_nerve_carpal_tunnel_syndrome": "Dareemaha median (cudurka carpal tunnel)",
      "carpal_tunnel_syndrome_is_compression_": "Cudurka carpal tunnel waa cadaadinta dareemaha median ee ka hooseeya flexor retinaculum curcurka. Dareemaha median wuxuu siiyaa suulka iyo 3.5 farood ee hore dareen. Isticmaalka soo noqnoqda ee curcurka waa qatar weyn.",
      "the_swollen_neck_node": "Node Qoorta oo Barara",
      "what_diagnosis_must_be_urgently_ruled_": "Baaritaankee ayaa si degdeg ah looga saarayaa?",
      "lymphoma_hodgkin_lymphoma": "Lymphoma (Hodgkin lymphoma)",
      "painless_lymphadenopathy_with_b_sympto": "Bararka qanjidhada lymph oo aan xanuun lahayn, oo leh calaamadaha B (dhidid habeen, miisaan yaraan, qandho) waa astaanta caadiga ah ee Hodgkin lymphoma dhallinyarada. Biopsy muujinaya unugyada Reed-Sternberg wuxuu xaqiijiyaa baaritaanka.",
      "the_diabetic_emergency": "Xaaladda Degdegga ee Sonkorowga",
      "which_cells_failed_and_what_is_the_eme": "Unugyadee ayaa fashilmay, waana maxay xaaladda degdegga ah?",
      "beta_cells_of_islets_of_langerhans_dia": "Unugyada beta ee islets of Langerhans; Diabetic Ketoacidosis (DKA)",
      "without_insulin_from_beta_cells_glucos": "Insulin la’aan oo unugyada beta ka timaada, glucose ma geli karo unugyada. Jirku wuxuu gubaa dufanka, isagoo soo saaraya ketones kuwaas oo dhiigga ka dhigaya aashito. Neefsashada Kussmaul waxay magdhabaan iyada oo la saarayo CO2. Daaweyn: dareere IV, insulin drip, iyo beddelka electrolyte.",
      "the_broken_collarbone": "Lafta Garabka oo Jabtay",
      "why_is_the_middle_third_of_the_clavicl": "Maxay saddex-meelaha dhexe ee clavicle u tahay meesha ugu badan jabka?",
      "the_middle_third_is_thinnest_and_has_n": "Saddex-meelaha dhexe ayaa ugu khafiifsan mana laha xoojin muruq",
      "the_clavicle_is_the_most_frequently_fr": "Clavicle waa lafta ugu badan jabka. Saddex-meelaha dhexe ayaa ugu khafiifsan mana laha ilaalin muruq. Xoogga ka yimaada dhicitaanka gacan fidsan wuxuu ku uruuraa meeshan daciifka ah. Inta badan waxay ku bogsadaan xidhitaan gacan.",
      "breathless_at_high_altitude": "Neefla’aan Meel Sarreysa",
      "why_does_altitude_cause_these_symptoms": "Maxay sarreynta u keentaa calaamadahan, qaab-dhismeedkee ayaana ugu cadaadis badan?",
      "the_alveoli_and_respiratory_muscles_re": "Alveoli iyo muruqyada neefsashada; oksijiinta jawiga oo yaraatay waxay keentaa hypoxia",
      "at_high_altitude_atmospheric_pressure_": "Meel sarreysa, cadaadiska jawigu wuu hoos u dhacaa, isagoo yaraynaya cadaadiska qayb ee oksijiinta. Oksijiin yar ayaa maraysa xuubka alveoli. Jirku wuu magdhabaa isagoo si degdeg ah oo qoto dheer u neefsanaya, isagoo kordhinaya shaqada muruqa neefsashada.",
