      "dna_genetics_lab": "🧬 DNA / Shaybaarka Genetics",
      "build_replicate_transcribe_translate_m": "Dhis • Nuqul • Qor • Turjun • Isbeddel • CRISPR • Sayniska garsoorka",
      "build_the_double_helix_from_4_letters": "Ka dhis double helix 4 xaraf",
      "a_pairs_with_t_2_bonds_g_with_c_3_wats": "A wuxuu la lammaanaa T (2 bond), G wuxuu la lammaanaa C (3). Watson + Crick + Franklin (1953) waxay ka xalliyeen qaabkan X-ray crystallography. Qaabkaas wuxuu muujinayaa sida DNA isu nuqulo oo loo akhriyo.",
      "replicate_unzip_copy_rezip": "Nuqul — fur, nuqul, mar labaad xir",
      "helicase_splits_the_strands_dna_polyme": "Helicase wuxuu kala qaybiyaa strand-yada; DNA polymerase wuxuu dhisaa strand dhammaystiran. Semi-conservative — helix cusub kastaa wuxuu leeyahay strand hore mid + mid cusub. Meselson iyo Stahl waxay caddeeyeen tan 1958.",
      "transcribe_dna_mrna_in_the_nucleus": "Qor — DNA → mRNA (nucleus gudaha)",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_one_dna_strand_3_": "RNA polymerase wuxuu akhriyaa DNA strand 3′→5′ wuxuuna dhisaa RNA 5′→3′. Xarfuhu waa isku mid, kaliya T wuxuu noqdaa U. mRNA wuxuu qaataa cunto-karinta ilaa ribosome — tallaabada koowaad ee central dogma.",
      "translate_mrna_protein_at_the_ribosome": "Turjun — mRNA → protein (ribosome-ka)",
      "64_codons_20_amino_acids_the_genetic_c": "codon 64 → amino acid 20 (genetic code way badan tahay). AUG wuu bilaabaa; UAA/UAG/UGA way joojiyaan. tRNA wuu akhriyaa codon, keenaa amino acid saxda ah, dhisaa peptide bond.",
      "mutate_substitution_insertion_deletion": "Isbeddel — bedelid, gelin, tirtirid",
      "point_mutation_one_letter_swapped_inse": "Point mutation — hal xaraf ayaa la beddelay. Insertion/deletion — reading frame wuu dhaqaaqaa, protein-ka hoose oo dhan wuu kharibmaa. Sickle cell anemia waa hal A→T oo keliya — hal xaraf, saameyn nolol oo dhan.",
      "crispr_the_precision_edit": "CRISPR — tafatir sax ah",
      "bacterial_immune_system_repurposed_cas": "Nidaamka difaaca bakteeriyada ayaa dib loo isticmaalay. Cas9 enzyme + guide RNA = maqas molecular ah. Doudna + Charpentier waxay ku guuleysteen Nobel 2020. CRISPR therapy-gii ugu horreeyay (sickle cell) FDA waxay ansixisay Diseembar 2023.",
      "protein_fold_function_malfunction": "Protein — laalaab, shaqo, cillad",
      "sequence_determines_structure_determin": "Sequence wuxuu go'aamiyaa qaab-dhismeedka kaas oo go'aamiya shaqada. Hemoglobin wuxuu qaadaa O₂, antibody way aqoonsadaan, enzyme way catalyze. AlphaFold (2020) wuxuu saadaaliyay qaab-dhismeed 200 milyan — dhibaato 50 sano ah waxaa la xalliyay 18 bilood gudahood.",
      "forensics_str_profiling_dna_evidence": "Sayniska garsoorka — STR profiling + caddayn DNA",
      "codis_uses_20_short_tandem_repeat_str_": "CODIS wuxuu isticmaalaa short tandem repeat (STR) loci 20. Suurtagalnimada isbarbaryaacaanka waa mid quadrillion marka loci-yada oo dhan is-waafaqaan. Innocence Project — xukumaad ka badan 245 oo qalad ah ayaa la burinayay tijaabada DNA dembiga kadib.",
      "challenge_graded_problems": "Caqabad — dhibaatooyin la qiimeeyay",
      "practice_transcription_translation_mut": "Ku celceli transcription, translation, kala-saarista mutation. AP Bio Big Idea 3.A.1 — DNA (marmar RNA) waa saldhigga gudbinta macluumaadka hidaha. NGSS HS-LS3-1.",
      "battle_head_to_head_retrieval": "Dagaal — soo-ceshasho wejiga-wejiga",
      "retrieval_practice_gamified_speed_buil": "Ku-celcelinta soo-ceshashada — qaab ciyaar. Xawaaraha wuxuu dhisaa automaticity — marka eegista codon table ay noqoto mid iskeed u dhacda, working memory-gaagu wuxuu noqdaa mid xor ah fikirka heerka sare, sida saadaalinta saameynta mutation.",
      "learn_the_central_dogma_history": "Baro — central dogma + taariikh",
      "dna_rna_protein_with_retroviruses_hiv_": "DNA → RNA → protein — oo ay ku jiraan retrovirus (HIV) oo dib u socda reverse transcriptase. Crick wuxuu abuuray erayga \"dogma\" 1957; markii dambe wuxuu yiri macneheedu waa mala-awaal, ma aha run aan la dafiri karin.",
      "build_a_dna_strand": "Dhis DNA strand",
      "pick_a_sequence_the_complementary_stra": "Dooro sequence — strand dhammaystiran waxaa lagu buuxiyaa base pairing (A-T, G-C). DNA dhabta ah sidan ayaa had iyo jeer loo dhisaa.",
      "dna_replication": "DNA replication",
      "helicase_unwinds_the_helix_dna_polymer": "Helicase wuxuu furaa helix; DNA polymerase wuxuu akhriyaa template strand kasta oo dhigaa dhammaystirkiisa. Semi-conservative — daughter strand kastaa wuxuu leeyahay hore mid + cusub mid.",
      "transcription_dna_mrna": "Transcription — DNA → mRNA",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_the_template_stra": "RNA polymerase wuxuu akhriyaa template strand. Sharcigii isku midka ahaa ee complementarity, laakiin T → U. Natiijada — hal mRNA copy oo single-strand ah, oo diyaar u ah inuu ka baxo nucleus.",
      "translation_mrna_protein": "Translation — mRNA → protein",
      "ribosome_reads_codons_3_bases_at_a_tim": "Ribosome wuxuu akhriyaa codon (base 3 mar walba). codon kasta → amino acid mid. Genetic code waxaa loo akhriyaa triplet aan is-dul-saarnayn, aan haysan comma.",
      "mutations": "Isbeddellada",
      "point_mutations_silent_no_protein_chan": "Point mutation — silent (protein ma beddelmo), missense (amino acid mid ka duwan), nonsense (joojin hore). Frameshift (insertion/deletion) inta badan waa mid wax kharribta.",
      "crispr_cas9_editing": "CRISPR-Cas9 editing",
      "guide_rna_points_cas9_to_a_20_base_tar": "Guide RNA wuxuu tilmaamaa Cas9 target 20-base ah. Cas9 wuxuu gooyaa labada strand. Repair pathway-yada unugga waxay xiraan hidde ama waxay ku daraan template aad bixisay.",
      "protein_structure": "Qaab-dhismeedka protein",
      "primary_sequence_secondary_helix_sheet": "Primary (sequence) → secondary (α-helix, β-sheet) → tertiary (laalaab 3D) → quaternary (multi-subunit). Beddelka hal amino acid wuu kharribi karaa laalaabka.",
      "dna_forensics": "DNA forensics",
      "str_profiling_13_20_short_tandem_repea": "STR profiling — short tandem repeat loci 13-20. Suurtagalnimada isbarbaryaacaanka aan kala sooc lahayn loci-yada oo dhan waa qiyaastii mid bilyan. Waxaa lagu isticmaalaa CODIS, paternity test, iyo forensic lab.",
      "daily_challenge": "Caqabadda maalinlaha ah",
      "a_new_dna_puzzle_every_session_transla": "Halxiraale DNA cusub session kasta. Turjun, aqoonso mutation, hel ORF ama xalli kiis forensic ah. Streak counter wuxuu la socdaa guusha maalinlaha ah.",
      "codon_battle": "Codon battle",
      "speed_translation_duel_decode_codons_f": "Tartan xawaare turjumaad. Decode codon si dhakhso ah adigoo la tartamaya saacadda. Tijaabi in genetic code uu maskaxdaada ku jiro, ee aan reference card oo keliya ku jirin.",
      "reference_glossary": "Tixraac + qaamuus",
