      "cell_surface_molecules_that_present_an": "cell surface molecule oo u soo bandhigaya antigen T cell. MHC I (unugyada oo dhan, viral peptide). MHC II (immune cell, extracellular peptide).",
      "plasma_proteins_that_punch_holes_in_pa": "plasma protein oo ka daloosha pathogen + qorta phagocyte.",
      "signaling_molecules_of_immune_system_i": "signaling molecule ee immune system. Interferon (antiviral), interleukin (isku-dubbarid), TNF (barar).",
      "long_lived_b_t_cells_from_prior_exposu": "B + T cell cimri dheer oo ka yimid soo-gaadhis hore. Saldhigga vaccine + difaac nolol oo dhan.",
      "train_adaptive_immunity_without_diseas": "Waxay tababaraan adaptive immunity cudur la'aan. mRNA (COVID), protein subunit, live attenuated, inactivated.",
      "immune_system_attacks_self_type_1_diab": "Immune system wuxuu weeraraa naftiisa. Type 1 diabetes, RA, MS, lupus, Hashimoto.",
      "ige_mediated_hypersensitivity_mast_cel": "IgE-mediated hypersensitivity. Mast cell waxay sii daayaan histamine.",
      "dendrites_receive_soma_cell_body_axon_": "Dendrite (helaan), soma (cell body), axon (dira), terminal (sii daaya neurotransmitter).",
      "all_or_none_electrical_signal_sodium_i": "All-or-none electrical signal. Sodium gudaha → depolarize → potassium dibadda → repolarize. ~1 ms. Speed — ~1 m/s (unmyelinated) ilaa ~100 m/s (myelinated).",
      "fatty_insulation_made_by_glia_oligoden": "Insulation dufan ah oo ay sameeyeen glia (oligodendrocyte CNS, Schwann cell PNS). Wuxuu dedejiyaa conduction. Wuxuu ku baabba'aa MS.",
      "junction_between_neurons_electrical_or": "junction u dhexeeya neuron. Electrical ama chemical (inta badan). Gap ~0.02 µm.",
      "chemical_messengers_across_synapse_exc": "chemical messenger synapse. Excitatory (glutamate), inhibitory (GABA), modulatory (serotonin, dopamine).",
      "reward_motivation_motor_control_low_in": "Reward, motivation, motor control. Hooseeya Parkinson; dysregulated schizophrenia.",
      "mood_sleep_appetite_ssris_target_reupt": "Mood, hurdo, cunto-doonis. SSRI waxay bartilmaameedsadaan reuptake.",
      "neuromuscular_junction_memory_attentio": "Neuromuscular junction. Memory + attention. Hooseeya Alzheimer.",
      "astrocytes_support_bbb_oligodendrocyte": "Astrocyte (support, BBB), oligodendrocyte (myelin CNS), microglia (immune), ependymal cell (cerebrospinal fluid).",
      "cerebrum_cortex_thinking_perception_ce": "Cerebrum (cortex — fikir, perception), cerebellum (motor coordination), brainstem (autonomic), limbic system (shucuur + memory).",
      "brain_reorganizes_itself_strongest_in_": "Maskaxdu waxay dib isu habaysaa — ugu xoog badan carruurnimada, laakiin way sii socotaa nolol oo dhan. Saldhigga learning.",
      "tight_junctions_between_brain_capillar": "tight junction u dhexeeya brain capillary cell waxay dibadda ku hayaan inta badan molecule. Caqabad weyn drug delivery ilaa CNS.",
      "20_of_body_s_energy_at_rest_despite_be": "~20% tamarta jirka marka nasto (inkastoo ay tahay ~2% mass). Inta badan Na+/K+ pump oo ilaaliya ion gradient.",
      "first_mass_produced_human_protein_made": "Protein bini'aadam ugu horreeya oo si tiro badan loo soo saaray. Waxaa lagu sameeyay E. coli (1982). Wuxuu beddelay insulin doofaar + lo'.",
      "single_target_therapies_humira_autoimm": "Single-target therapy. Humira (autoimmune), Herceptin (HER2+ breast cancer), Keytruda (immunotherapy).",
      "covid_19_vaccines_pfizer_moderna_self_": "COVID-19 vaccine (Pfizer, Moderna). Self-amplifying version + non-COVID application horumar ku jira.",
      "replace_defective_genes_luxturna_inher": "Waxay beddelaan hidde cillad leh. Luxturna (indho-la'aan dhaxal, FDA 2017). Zolgensma (SMA, 2019).",
