      "sing_into_the_mic_the_lab_tracks_frequ": "Ku hees makarafoonka; shaybaadhku wuxuu la socdaa inta-jeer waqtiga dhabta ah. Heesaayaasha la tababaray waxay ku hayaan dhawaaqa codka gudaha ±5 cents (1/20 nuska-codka) — sidan ayuu u dhawaaqaa cod-waafajin dhammaystiran.",
