      "sight_reading_2": "Akhrinta Qoraalka",
      "solf_ge_do_re_mi_letter_names_for_sigh": "Solfège (do-re-mi) way ka fiican tahay magacyada xarfaha akhrinta qoraalka sababtoo ah shaqallada waxay siraan xiriirrada farqiga codka, ee ma aha oo keliya astaamaha dhawaaqa codka. Do socda way ka fiican tahay do go'an muusikada codka leh.",
