      "interior_angle_sum_n_2_180_for_any_n_s": "Wadarta xagalka gudaha = (n − 2) × 180° badan-gees kasta oo n-dhinac ah. Xagal kasta oo dibadda ah oo badan-gees CAADI ah = 360°/n. Wadarta xaglaha dibadda had iyo jeer = 360°.",
      "sin_trigonometric_functions": "sin Hawlaha trigonometrik",
      "soh_cah_toa_sine_opp_hyp_cosine_adj_hy": "SOH-CAH-TOA: Sine = Ka-soo-horjeeda/Hypotenuse, Cosine = Dhinac/Hypotenuse, Tangent = Ka-soo-horjeeda/Dhinac. Hawlaha trig waxay muujiyaan saamiyada dhinacyada saddex-geeska qumman; waxaa lagu fidiyay dhammaan xaglaha iyada oo la adeegsanayo goobada cutubka.",
