      "three_views_of_the_same_trigonometric_": "Saddex aragti oo isku dejin trigonometrik ah. Jiid sliderka xagalka (ama dhererka munaaradda) — matalaad kastaa isla mar bay is-cusbooneysiisaa. Kadibna qaado imtixaanka dhibaatada-rogan: xallo cabbir dhab ah adigoo isticmaalaya hal matalaad kaliya.",
