      "circle_has_most_area_for_a_perimeter": "Goobadu waxay leedahay aagga ugu badan wareega la siiyay",
      "isoperimetric_inequality_4_a_p_equalit": "Sinnaan-la'aanta isoperimetric: 4πA ≤ P². Sinnaan kaliya goobooyinka. Sababta xumbada saabuunta + meerayaashu u wareegsan yihiin.",
      "sphere_has_most_volume_for_a_surface_a": "Kuraydhku waxay leedahay mugga ugu badan aagga dusha la siiyay",
      "3d_version_of_above_single_bubbles_are": "Nooca 3D ee kore. Xumbooyinka keli ah waa kuraydho; xumbooyinka isku dhafan waxay ku kulmaan xaglo 120°.",
      "regular_hexagons_tile_most_efficiently": "Lix-geesyada caadiga ah ayaa si ugu hufan u turxaamiya",
