        "input_image_alt": "Badhanka sawirka wuxuu maqan yahay qoraal alt. Isticmaalayaasha akhriyaha shaashadda ma garan doonaan waxa uu badhanku qabto.",
        "button_name": "Badhanku ma laha magac uu akhriyaha shaashadda u dhawaaqi karo. Ardayga wuxuu maqli lahaa kaliya \"button\" la'aan macno.",
